%2F80-detained-after-raid-at-rave-party-in-maharashtras-thane-drugs-seized-4774385%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F80-detained-after-raid-at-rave-party-in-maharashtras-thane-drugs-seized-4774385%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F80-detained-after-raid-at-rave-party-in-maharashtras-thane-drugs-seized-4774385%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teachers%20of%20Murdered%20Indian-Origin%20Teen%20Express%20Grief%2C%20Say%20She%20Was%20'Brilliant'%2C%20'Amazing%20Singer'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETeachers%20and%20classmates%20of%20an%2018-year-old%20Indian-origin%20teen%20who%20was%20found%20dead%20along%20with%20her%20parents%20in%20Massachusetts%20remember%20her%20as%20a%20brilliant%20student%20and%20an%20amazing%20singer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20Arianna%20Kamal%2C%20and%20her%20parents%20Rakesh%20Kamal%20and%20Teena%20Kamal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwealthy-indian-origin-couple-daughter-found-dead-at-their-us-home-police-suspect-domestic-violence-4768218%5C%22%3Ewere%20found%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20%245%20million%20Dover%20mansion%20in%20an%20apparent%20domestic%20violence%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDover%20is%2032%20km%20from%20downtown%20Boston%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArianna%20was%20a%20student%20of%20Middlebury%20College.%20The%20college%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20she%20was%20participating%20in%20a%20first-year%20seminar%2C%20Mindfulness%20in%20Education%2C%20taught%20by%20Melissa%20Hammerle%2C%20the%20visiting%20assistant%20professor%20of%20education%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArianna%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20an%20organisation%20for%20students%20with%20an%20interest%20in%20foraging%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Women%20in%20Computer%20Science%20student%20organisation%2C%20the%20college%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20loved%20singing%20and%20was%20interested%20in%20going%20to%20Italy%20with%20the%20college%20opera%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Melissa%2C%20who%20taught%20the%20Indian-origin%20teen%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAria%20was%20beloved%20by%20the%20college%20choir%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20music%20teacher%20Jeffrey%20Buettner.%20%26quot%3BShe%20loved%20singing%20together%2C%20and%20her%20choir%20community%20was%20deeply%20meaningful%20to%20her%20in%20her%20first%20semester.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20college%20said%20once%20it%20returns%20from%20the%20break%2C%20it%20will%20work%20with%20Aria's%20friends%20and%20possibly%20with%20her%20extended%20family%20to%20plan%20an%20appropriate%20remembrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20this%20news%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20those%20who%20knew%20Aria%2C%20those%20with%20experiences%20of%20domestic%20violence%2C%20those%20grieving%20other%20losses%2C%20and%20for%20our%20whole%20community%2C%20especially%20as%20most%20of%20us%20are%20apart%20from%20our%20Middlebury%20campus%20community%20during%20winter%20break%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20college%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArianna%20had%20graduated%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Milton%20Academy%20this%20summer.%20The%20school%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20sweet%2C%20smart%2C%20kind%20young%20woman%20who%20was%20just%20beginning%20to%20realize%20her%20full%20potential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%2C%20Teena%2C%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20school%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMilton%20Academy%20is%20heartbroken%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Arianna%20Kamal%2C%20a%20recent%20graduate%20of%20the%20class%20of%202023%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20deaths%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20Rakesh%20Kamal%20and%20Teena%20Kamal.%20Our%20thoughts%20are%20with%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Kamal%20family%2C%20their%20friends%20and%20our%20entire%20school%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20full%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20also%20went%20by%20Rick%2C%20had%20previously%20run%20a%20now-defunct%20education%20systems%20company%20called%20EduNova.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kamals%20had%20purchased%20the%2019%2C000-square-foot%20estate%20-%20which%20boasts%2011%20bedrooms%20-%20for%20%244%20million%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%20The%20family%20members%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20living%20in%20the%20mansion%20at%20the%20time%20in%20the%20area%2C%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20company%20was%20launched%20in%202016%20but%20was%20dissolved%20in%20December%202021%2C%20state%20records%20show.%20Teena%20was%20listed%20on%20EduNova's%20website%20as%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20company%2C%20describing%20her%20as%20an%20alum%20of%20Harvard%20University%20and%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704007020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fo76vc084_indian-origin-family_625x300_31_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fteachers-of-murdered-indian-origin-teen-arianna-kamal-express-grief-say-she-was-brilliant-amazing-singer-4774353%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Teachers%20and%20classmates%20of%20an%2018-year-old%20Indian-origin%20teen%20who%20was%20found%20dead%20along%20with%20her%20parents%20in%20Massachusetts%20remember%20her%20as%20a%20brilliant%20student%20and%20an%20amazing%20singer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fteachers-of-murdered-indian-origin-teen-arianna-kamal-express-grief-say-she-was-brilliant-amazing-singer-4774353%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fteachers-of-murdered-indian-origin-teen-arianna-kamal-express-grief-say-she-was-brilliant-amazing-singer-477435