C000-tonne%20INS%20Vikrant%20was%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20and%20was%20commissioned%20in%20September%20last%20year.%20At%20262%20metres%20long%20and%2062%20metres%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20have%2030%20aircraft%20on%20board%2C%20including%20MiG-29K%20fighter%20jets%20and%20helicopters.%20The%20warship%20can%20accommodate%20a%20crew%20of%20nearly%201%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20started%20negotiations%20with%20France%20for%20the%20acquisition%20of%2026%20Rafale-M%20aircraft%20which%20are%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20MiG-29Ks%20onboard%20the%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warship%20was%20in%20the%20works%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20Multiple%20phases%20of%20sea%20trials%20of%20INS%20Vikrant%20have%20been%20completed%20since%20August%2021%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20INS%20Vikrant%2C%20India%20has%20joined%20a%20select%20group%20of%20nations%2C%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Russia%2C%20China%20and%20France%2C%20that%20can%20design%20and%20build%20their%20own%20aircraft%20carriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704005880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fkr000vpg_ins-vikrant_625x300_31_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fins-vikrant-feels-good-to-ins-vikrants-post-after-getting-new-radar-missiles-4773988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22INS%20Vikrant%2C%20India's%20first%20indigenous%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20is%20now%20equipped%20with%20a%20sophisticated%20guidance%20radar%20and%20surface%20to%20air%20missiles%20-%20a%20move%20seen%20as%20a%20crucial%20step%20towards%20its%20operational%20deployment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fins-vikrant-feels-good-to-ins-vikrants-post-after-getting-new-radar-missiles-4773988%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fins-vikrant-feels-good-to-ins-vikrants-post-after-getting-new-radar-missiles-4773988%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fins-vikrant-feels-good-to-ins-vikrants-post-after-getting-new-radar-missiles-4773988%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Indian%20Airlines'%20Safety%20Check%20On%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20After%20Loose%20Bolt%20Alert%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20alert%20over%20a%20loose%20bolt%20in%20new-built%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20passenger%20aircraft%20has%20prompted%20airlines%20in%20India%20which%20operate%20the%20type%20to%20carry%20out%20checks%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20no%20defects%20that%20can%20affect%20flight%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20aviation%20regulator%2C%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%2C%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20and%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Akasa%2C%20Air%20India%20Express%20and%20SpiceJet%2C%20which%20operate%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20US'%20Federation%20Aviation%20Administration%20said%20it%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20targeted%20inspections%20of%20Boeing%20737%20MAX%20airplanes%20to%20look%20for%20a%20possible%20loose%20bolt%20in%20the%20rudder%20control%20system.%20The%20plane%20manufacturer%20has%20said%20the%20issue%20identified%20on%20a%20particular%20aircraft%20has%20been%20fixed%20and%20asked%20airlines%20to%20conduct%20an%20inspection%20of%20their%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGCA%20has%20said%20it%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20its%20US%20counterpart%20and%20Boeing%20and%20that%20the%20checks%20currently%20being%20carried%20out%20are%20part%20of%20the%20regular%20process%20to%20ensure%20flight%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20an%20ongoing%20issue%20with%20Max%20737%20and%20these%20are%20service%20bulletins%20issued%20from%20time%20to%20time%20by%20Boeing%20to%20the%20airline%20operators%20for%20the%20suggested%20action%20whenever%20any%20issue%20is%20come%20across.%20We%20have%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Boeing%2C%20FAA%20and%20our%20airline%20operators%20in%20the%20past%20too%20on%20such%20issues%20concerning%20737%20Max%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DGCA%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20such%20cases%2C%20mitigation%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%20Original%20Equipment%20Manufacturers%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20airline%20operator%20as%20has%20been%20done%20in%20the%20past%20in%20respect%20of%20737%20Max%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Akasa%20Air%20spokesperson%20has%20said%20Boeing%20had%20informed%20them%20about%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BLike%20all%20operators%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20highest%20standards%20of%20safety%2C%20Akasa%20will%20be%20following%20the%20same%20checks%20and%20procedures%20that%20the%20manufacturer%20or%20regulator%20recommends.%20Our%20operating%20fleet%20and%20deliveries%20are%20not%20impacted%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Air%20India%20Express%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20per%20Boeing's%20global%20recommendation%20for%20all%20airline%20operators%2C%20Air%20India%20Express%20will%20check%20its%20Boeing%20737-8%20aircraft%20within%20the%20timelines.%20Our%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20safety%20remains%20paramount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20SpiceJet%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20fresh%20alert%20will%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20its%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airlines%20NDTV%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20say%20the%20inspection%20does%20not%20take%20more%20than%202%20hours%20per%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20737%20Max%2C%20the%20manufacturer's%20fastest-selling%20plane%20in%20history%2C%20was%20grounded%20worldwide%20in%202019%20after%20crashes%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20Jakarta%20left%20356%20people%20dead.%20The%20aircraft%20was%20back%20in%20service%20early%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%2