%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20instructive%20that%20six%20of%20the%20nine%20films%20and%20shows%20listed%20here%20are%20based%20on%20true-life%20stories.%20And%20even%20those%20that%20are%20fictional%20are%20close%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20front%20line%20among%20my%20favourite%20films%20was%20one%20that%20came%20early%20in%20the%20year%2C%20Nandita%20Das%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EZwigato%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20narrative%20of%20aching%20tenderness%20and%20gentle%20rage.%20Das%20carefully%20observes%20the%20quiet%20struggles%2C%20the%20dignity%2C%20the%20resolve%2C%20the%20hurt%20and%20the%20determined%20love%20of%20Manas%20Mahto%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20food%20delivery%20man%2C%20and%20Pratima%20who%20steps%20out%20warily%20to%20share%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20burdens%2C%20as%20a%20masseuse%20to%20rich%20women%20in%20high-rise%20apartments%20and%20as%20a%20janitor%20in%20a%20mall.%20With%20luminous%20empathy%2C%20Kapil%20Sharma%20and%20Shahana%20Goswami%20portray%20how%20both%20try%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20other%20from%20the%20humiliations%2C%20the%20insults%20and%20disappointments%20that%20they%20endure%20as%20they%20daily%20grapple%20with%20the%20uncaring%2C%20unequal%20world%20of%20rich%20and%20middle-class%20India.%20Their%20unostentatious%20but%20steadfast%20love%20for%20each%20other%20and%20for%20those%20in%20their%20care%20forms%20the%20moral%20core%20of%20the%20film%2C%20and%20in%20the%20end%20its%20only%20fount%20of%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads