ssively%20pursue%20justice%20from%20the%20courts.%20The%20criminal%20cases%20against%20the%20cinema%20owners%2C%20the%20Ansal%20brothers%2C%20who%20had%20violated%20elementary%20safety%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20managers%20of%20the%20theatre%20move%20at%20a%20glacial%20pace%20through%20the%20Kafkaesque%20maze%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20system.%20In%20the%20end%20the%20courts%20let%20off%20those%20criminally%20guilty%20of%20causing%20so%20many%20deaths%20all%20too%20lightly.%20Justice%20fails%20Neelam%20and%20Shekhar%2C%20but%20they%20are%20victorious%20in%20the%20ways%20they%20uphold%20the%20tenacity%20of%20the%20human%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691079%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Trial%20By%20Fire%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20idealism%20and%20courage%20again%20that%20powers%20another%20true-life%20story%20of%20a%20small-town%20unassuming%20lawyer%20who%20fought%20for%20justice%20for%20a%20girl%20who%20was%20sexually%20abused%20by%20a%20powerful%20godman%20with%20a%20huge%20empire%2C%20in%20Apoorv%20Singh%20Karki%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ESirf%20Ek%20Banda%20Hi%20Kaafi%20Hai.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20film%20does%20little%20to%20disguise%20the%20factual%20story%20of%20Asaram%20Bapu%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20influential%20gurus%20who%20founded%20over%20400%20ashrams%20in%20India%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20who%20wielded%20formidable%20political%20clout.%20He%20was%20charged%20with%20rape%20by%20a%2016-year-old%20daughter%20of%20two%20of%20his%20devotees%20who%20he%20took%20into%20his%20room%20claiming%20to%20cure%20her%20of%20evil%20spirits.%20The%20battle%20was%20fought%20spiritedly%20by%20a%20little-known%20lawyer%20in%20Jodhpur.%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%20plays%20to%20perfection%20this%20lawyer%20whose%20politics%20leans%20to%20the%20right%20but%20who%20is%20compelled%20by%20a%20fierce%20devotion%20to%20justice%20to%20fight%20some%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20people%20in%20the%20land%20to%20secure%20ultimately%20a%20life%20sentence%20for%20the%20godman.%20Among%20the%20endearing%20sequences%20in%20the%20film%20are%20when%20he%20argues%20in%20court%20against%20senior%20lawyers%20%E2%80%93%20in%20real-life%20Ram%20Jethmalani%2C%20Salman%20Khurshid%20and%20Subramaniam%20Swamy%20%E2%80%93%20hired%20by%20the%20godman.%20Bajpayee%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20combines%20in%20these%20moments%20fanboy%20awe%20and%20veneration%20for%20these%20legendary%20seniors%20with%20a%20brave%20and%20robust%20commitment%20to%20his%20calling%20and%20the%20righteousness%20of%20his%20cause.%20He%20is%20empathetic%20and%20supportive%20to%20the%20girl%2C%20and%20he%20does%20not%20flinch%20even%20after%20a%20series%20of%20key%20witnesses%20are%20murdered%20and%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20his%20life%20is%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdealism%20is%20what%20also%20sustains%20the%20central%20protagonist%20in%20Vidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E12th%C2%A0Fail%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eanother%20exhilarating%20real-life%20story%20of%20a%20young%20man%20from%20a%20remote%20village%20in%20the%20Chambal%20region%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(Manoj%20Kumar%20Sharma)%20who%20fights%20incredible%20odds%20to%20qualify%20finally%20in%20the%20most%20fiercely%20contested%20competitive%20examination%20in%20the%20country%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer.%20As%20a%20young%20man%20he%20meets%20a%20police%20officer%20who%20is%20honest%2C%20kind%20and%20just.%20This%20encounter%20alters%20the%20course%20of%20his%20life.%20It%20is%20the%20dream%20to%20become%20a%20police%20officer%20like%20him%20that%20drives%20him%20to%20the%20city%2C%20where%20he%20survives%20through%20years%20of%20hard%20manual%20labour%2C%20disappointments%20and%20setbacks%20to%20study%20for%20the%20examination.%20He%20persists%20to%20rise%20again%20and%20again%20against%20defeat%20and%20hardship%2C%20to%20finally%20overcome.%20Vikram%20Massey%20brings%20a%20rare%20sensitivity%20and%20authenticity%20to%20his%20portrayal%2C%20raising%20him%20to%20the%20top%20rung%20of%20our%20actors.%20It%20is%20hard%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20forget%20the%20sequence%20in%20the%20film%20when%20his%20friend%20tells%20him%20that%20he%20has%20qualified%20in%20the%20examination%2C%20and%20he%20just%20crumbles%20into%20a%20heap%20on%20the%20ground%20overcome%20with%20emotion.%20I%20wanted%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20cheer%20in%20a%20scene%20near%20the%20end%20when%2C%20Massey%E2%80%99s%20character%2C%20now%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20drives%20to%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Chambal%20to%20meet%20the%20policeman%20who%20years%20earlier%20had%20inspired%20him.%20The%20young%20officer%20touches%20his%20feet%2C%20the%20older%20man%20proudly%20salutes%20the%20man%20who%20is%20now%20his%20superior%20officer%2C%20and%20then%20they%20both%20embrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115802%2Fdownload-19.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20