has%20implications%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20programmes%20and%20estimations%20that%20the%20government%20and%20others%20make%20over%20needs%20of%20the%20population%2C%20as%20the%20Census%20is%20the%20largest%20public%20body%20of%20data%20about%20the%20country%20available%20and%20updated.%20It%20may%20even%20render%20those%20seen%20as%20needing%20extra%20care%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20among%20the%20uncounted%20and%20therefore%20not%20helped%20by%20government%20schemes.%20The%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20passed%20in%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20is%20contingent%20on%20the%20next%20delimitation%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20the%20next%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Census%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20RGI%20and%20the%20Census%20Commissioner%20of%20India%20have%20also%20not%20released%20two%20important%20reports%20on%20the%20registration%20of%20births%2C%20deaths%2C%20and%20causes%20of%20deaths%20for%20the%20years%202021%2C%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%20that%20the%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F42542%5C%22%3EVital%20Statistics%20of%20India%20Based%20On%20The%20Civil%20Registration%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20for%202020%20was%20only%20released%20in%20May%202022.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20vital%20statistics%20are%20invaluable%20for%20planning%2C%C2%A0monitoring%20and%20evaluating%20various%20programmes%20related%20to%20primary%20health%20care%2C%20family%20planning%2C%C2%A0maternal%20and%20child%20health%2C%20education%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20cites%20the%20report%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F42681%2Fdownload%2F46350%2FAnnual_Report_on_MCCD_2020.pdf%5C%22%3EReport%20On%20Medical%20Certification%20Of%20Cause%20of%20Death%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20last%20released%20for%20the%20year%202020.%20This%20report%20carries%20statistics%20on%20the%20causes%20of%20deaths%2C%20cross-tabulating%20them%20by%20age%20and%20sex%20of%20the%20deceased.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20wide%20divergence%2C%20almost%20ten-fold%2C%20between%20India%E2%80%99s%20reported%20figures%20on%20COVID-19%20and%20that%20estimated%20globally%20by%20the%20WHO.%20The%20official%20document%20would%20bring%20more%20clarity%20on%20this%20but%20it%20remains%20unreleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704004202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-census-till-at-least-october-2024-ninth-extension-of-deadline-the-hindu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%222021%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20decennial%20census%20of%20India%20was%20postponed%20in%20150%20years.%20No%20report%20on%20births%2C%20deaths%20and%20causes%20of%20deaths%20has%20also%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20for%202021%2C%202022%20and%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-census-till-at-least-october-2024-ninth-extension-of-deadline-the-hindu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Please%20don't%20bother%20Jeff%20Bezos%20on%20vacation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20sailing%20yacht%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659108a1ec62ab5daf7fcc70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Bezos's%20megayacht%20%26quot%3BKoru%26quot%3B%20is%20seen%20docked%20at%20Port%20Everglades%20in%20Port%20Everglades%2C%20Florida.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJeff%20Bezos%20has%20been%20spending%20a%20lot%20of