trong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20the%20government%20was%20able%20to%20pass%20legislation%20okaying%20electoral%20bonds%20in%202018%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2015%2C956.3096%20crore%20have%20been%20sold.%20This%20has%20happened%20in%2029%20tranches.%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20has%20stated%20to%20transparency%20activist%20and%20war%20veteran%2C%20Commodore%20Lokesh%20Batra%20in%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20query%20filed%20by%20him%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fsbis-rti-reply-shows-electoral-bonds-worth-15-956-30-crore-sold-in-29-tranches-since-2018-11703753735516.html%5C%22%3Ereports%20%3Cem%3ELivemint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20the%20designated%20bank%2C%20authorised%20to%20issue%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%20has%20charged%20Rs%2013.50%20crore%20to%20the%20government%20towards%20its%20%E2%80%9Ccommission%2C%20printing%20and%20other%20expenses%20for%20managing%20and%20operating%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%E2%80%9D.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fgovt-spent-rs-13-50-cr-to-operate-electoral-bond-scheme-9089091%2F%5C%22%3ELokesh%20Batra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20irony%20of%20the%20scheme%20is%20that%20while%20donors%20are%20not%20required%20to%20pay%20any%20service%20charges%20(commission)%20to%20SBI%2C%20and%20even%20printing%20cost%20of%20EBs%2C%20it%20is%20the%20government%20or%20ultimately%20the%20tax%20payers%20who%20bear%20this%20cost%E2%80%A6for%20enabling%20transactions%20of%20anonymous%20tax-free%20funding%20to%20political%20parties%20through%20the%20opaque%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%202018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RTI%20has%20also%20revealed%20that%20of%20the%20total%20bonds%20that%20were%20sold%2C%20194%20bonds%20worth%C2%A0Rs%2023.8874%20crore%20were%20not%20encashed%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20getting%20transferred%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20National%20Relief%20Fund%20(PMNRF).%20Between%20April%202017%20and%20March%202022%2C%20the%20PMNRF%20had%20secured%20Rs%202%2C065.69%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20controversial%20source%20of%20funding%20political%20parties%20have%20come%20under%20flak%20by%20activists%20and%20opposition%20parties%20as%20being%20opaque%20and%20possibly%20routing%20unaccounted%20for%20money%20to%20political%20parties.%20Previously%2C%20there%20was%20a%20limit%20to%20the%20proportion%20of%20funds%20a%20company%20could%20give%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20but%20not%20anymore.%20The%20Modi%20government%20in%20hearings%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20four%20years%20after%20petitions%20were%20filed%2C%20pleaded%20to%20protect%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20big%20corporate%20donors%20to%20political%20parties.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20case%20on%20November%202%2C%202023.%20A%20former%20chief%20election%20commissioner%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Felectoral-bonds-supreme-court-must-uphold-right-to-information-9012313%2F%5C%22%3ES.Y.%20Qureshi%2C%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20citizens%20need%20not%20know%20about%20who%20was%20funding%20whom%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20disturbing%20to%20hear%20the%20argument%20of%20the%20SG%20that%20citizens%20have%20no%20right%20to%20know%20the%20donors%2Frecipients%E2%80%99%20identities.%20This%20statement%20would%20behove%20a%20banana%20republic%2C%20not%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20aspiring%20to%20be%20Vishwaguru.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20bonds%20can%20be%20purchased%20by%20any%20citizen%20of%20India%20or%20entity%20incorporated%20or%20established%20in%20the%20country.%20An%20individual%20can%20buy%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20either%20singly%20or%20jointly%2C%20with%20other%20individuals.%20Only%20registered%20political%20parties%20which%20secure%20not%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20votes%20polled%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20election%20are%20eligible%20to%20receive%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20in%202018%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20remained%20the%20net%20gainer%20by%20far%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20It%20has%20received%2057%25%20of%20the%C2%A0Rs%209%2C200%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bond%20funds%20while%20the%20Congress%20got%2010%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-11%2Fmodi-s-party-retains-top-spot-with-more-donations-than-rivals%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704002551000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F10170626%2Fsyed-hussaini-HlLno-CSbq8-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felectoral-bonds-worth-nearly-rs-16000-crore-since-2018-taxpayer-paid-rs-13-5-crore-as-commission-other-expenses-rti%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Transparency%20activist%20Commodore%20Lokesh%20Batra%20said%20it%20was%20odd%20that%20donors%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20this%20service%20charge%2C%20but%20government%20and%20ultimately%20the%20taxpayer%20has%20to%20pay%20up%20for%20these%20opaque%20sources%20of%20election%20funding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felectoral-bonds-worth-nearly-rs-16000-crore-since-2018-taxpayer-paid-rs-13-5-crore-as-commission-other-expenses-rti%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20MP's%20Brother%20Arrested%20In%20Karnataka%20After%20126%20Trees%20Worth%20Crores%20Felled%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20brother%20of%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%2C%20who%20hit%20headlines%20for%20the%20massive%20breach%20in%20Parliament%20security%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20worth%20crores.%C2%A0Vikram%20Simha%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20squad%20of%20Central%20Crime%20Branch%2C%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20forest%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20126%20trees%20worth%20crores%20were%20felled%20in%20Karnataka's%20Hassan%20district%20and%20transported%20elsewhere.%20An%20official%20report%20said%20%26quot%3Bavailable%20documentary%20evidence%26quot%3B%20hinted%20at%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime.%20Forest%20officials%20had%20been%20looking%20for%20Vikram%20Simha%2C%20but%20he%20escaped.%20The%20officials%20used%20electronic%20surveillance%20to%20track%20down%20Vikram%20to%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forest%20officials%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20team%20and%20Vikram%20Simha%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20joint%20operation.%20He%20will%20now%20be%20taken%20to%20Hassan%20for%20further%20action%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20his%20brother's%20arrest%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20brought%20up%20the%20cheque%20bounce%20case%20involving%20Karnataka%20minister%20Madhu%20Bangarappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMadhu%20Bangarappa%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20check%20bounce%20case%20worth%20Rs%206.5%20crore.%20That%20invites%20a%20jail%20term%20of%20six%20months%20by%20the%20court.%20But%20my%20brother%20is%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Simha%20questioned%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20if%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20sacrifice%20my%20family%20for%20your%20son's%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brother's%20arrest%20comes%20at%20a%20tough%20time%20for%20the%20BJP%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20already%20drawing%20fire%20from%20the%20Opposition%20after%20his%20name%20came%20up%20in%20the%20Parliament%20breach%20case.%20One%20of%20the%20intruders%20who%20trespassed%20into%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2013%20was%20carrying%20a%20visitor's%20pass%20issued%20by%20Pratap%20Simha's%20office.%20The%20BJP%20had%20later%20told%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20that%20the%20intruder's%20father%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20his%20constituency%20and%20had%20asked%20for%20a%20pass%20to%20visit%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20questioned%20why%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20Mr%20Simha%20yet%2C%20even%20though%20146%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20for%20unruly%20conduct%20after%20they%20demanded%20a%20statement%20from%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20massive%20security%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Simha%20recently%20said%20the%20people%20will%20decide%20if%20he%20was%20a%20patriot%20or%20a%20traitor%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20due%20next%20year.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20Pratap%20Simha%20is%20a%20traitor%20or%20a%20patriot%20--%20mother%20Goddess%20Chamundeshwari%20sitting%20on%20the%20hills%20of%20Mysuru%2C%20mother%20Goddess%20Cauvery%20who%20is%20sitting%20on%20Brahmagiri%2C%20my%20reader%20fans%20across%20Karnataka%20who%20have%20been%20reading%20my%20writings%20for%20the%20last%20twenty%20years%2C%20and%20people%20of%20Mysuru%20and%20Kodgu%20who%20have%20seen%20my%20work%20for%209.5%20years%20and%20my%20conduct%20on%20issues%20related%20country%2C%20dharma%20and%20nationalism%20--%20will%20give%20their%20verdict%20through%20votes%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20journalist-turned-politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20questioned%20why%20the%20BJP%20MP%20has%20not%20been%20questioned%20so%20far.%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%2C%20Mr%20Simha's%20statement%20had%20been%20recorded%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704002400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fn634qflg_pratap-simha-bro-split_625x300_31