2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13095447%2FIMG_0163.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20once%20again%20that%20time%20of%20the%20year%20when%20one%20cannot%20help%20taking%20stock%20of%20the%20human%20condition.%20A%20little%20over%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FOpinion%2F4SU2xQInFb2UxdQ2hkgH5J%2FIs-the-history-of-the-1930s-repeating-itself.html%5C%22%3Especulated%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20whether%20the%20history%20of%20the%20catastrophic%201930s%20that%20saw%20the%20rise%20of%20far%20right-wing%20regimes%20in%20Europe%20%C2%A0was%20about%20to%20repeat%20itself.%20While%20noting%20similarities%20with%20the%20present%2C%20including%20the%20culpability%20of%20old%20elites%20that%20facilitated%20the%20rise%20of%20charismatic%20right-wing%20populist%20leaders%2C%20I%20concluded%20that%20while%20history%20was%20unlikely%20to%20be%20repeated%20in%20the%20same%20manner%2C%20human%20tragedy%20of%20indeterminate%20magnitude%20was%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20totalitarian%20states%20in%20Europe%20in%20the%201930s%20preyed%20on%20their%20own%20citizens.%20The%20brunt%20of%20current%20right-wing%20extremism%20in%20the%20west%20was%20now%20likely%20to%20be%20felt%20by%20the%20large%20number%20of%20immigrants%20with%20no%20voting%20rights%2C%20from%20the%20developing%2C%20and%20particularly%20Muslim%2C%20world%2C%20fleeing%20right-wing%20regimes%20in%20their%20own%20countries.%20Classic%20fascist%20regimes%2C%20that%20target%20and%20polarise%20their%20own%20citizens%2C%20were%20more%20likely%20in%20developing%20countries%20where%20liberalism%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20institutions%20are%20still%20relatively%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20has%20happened%20over%20the%20last%20seven%20years%20%E2%80%93%20the%20tragedy%20unfolding%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20the%20continued%20triumphal%20march%20of%20the%20far%20right%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20of%20which%20the%20prospects%20of%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency%20in%20the%20US%20is%20emblematic%20%E2%80%93%20to%20allay%20these%20fears.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20continued%20inability%20of%20entrenched%20elites%20to%20address%20subaltern%20concerns%20of%20joblessness%2C%20particularly%20growing%20youth%20unemployment%2C%20and%20inequality%2C%20have%20amplified%20these%20fears.%20What%20has%20been%20clarified%20in%20the%20interim%20is%20that%20while%20it%20might%20not%20be%20very%20different%20in%20substance%2C%20the%20face%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20far%20right%20would%20be%20quite%20different%20from%20what%20it%20was%20a%20hundred%20years%20ago.%20Like%20old%20wine%20in%20new%20bottles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20lesson%20that%20the%20far%20right%20has%20learnt%20since%20is%20that%20given%20the%20hegemony%20of%20democratic%20ideas%20in%20civil%20society%2C%20formal%20institutions%20of%20state%20power%2C%20such%20as%20the%20constitution%2C%20extant%20laws%2C%20the%20judiciary%2C%20the%20ballot%20box%2C%20electoral%20machinery%2C%20the%20media%2C%20etc.%20cannot%20simply%20be%20cast%20aside%20like%20a%20century%20ago.%20Indeed%2C%20retaining%20the%20trappings%20of%20democracy%20as%20smokescreen%20while%20hollowing%20it%20out%20from%20inside%20by%20capturing%20its%20apparatus%20so%20that%20it%20works%20exclusively%20in%20your%20favour%2C%20enhances%20legitimacy.%20This%20is%20made%20possible%20by%20taking%20advantage%20of%20loopholes%20in%20the%20constitution%20or%20extant%20laws%20to%20appoint%20those%20you%20can%20somehow%20control%2C%20through%20shared%20ideology%2C%20and%20through%20carrot%20and%20stick%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Reflections%20on%20a%20Disturbing%20Year%20Gone%20By.%20And%20the%20Challenges%20That%20Lie%20Ahead.%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Freflections-on-a-disturbing-year-gone-by-and-the-challenges-that-lie-ahead%5C%22%3EReflections%20on%20a%20Disturbing%20Year%20Gone%20By.%20And%20the%20Challenges%20That%20Lie%20Ahead.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20big%20difference%20between%20the%20old%20and%20new%20far%20right%20lies%20in%20leveraging%20communication%20for%20mass%20mobilisation%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98post-truth%E2%80%99%20digital%20era.%20The%2020th%20century%20fascist%20dictatorships%20controlled%20the%20media%2C%20and%20through%20it%20information.%20The%20new%20right%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20control%20information%20in%20the%20digital%20age%20so%20injects%20instead%20a%20barrage%20of%20falsehoods%20and%20deep%20fakes%20into%20the%20public%20domain%20through%20social%20media%2C%20amplifying%20fear%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20doubt%20to%20win%20arguments%20through%20evidence%20and%20reason.%20George%20Orwell%20(%3Cem%3EAnimal%20Farm%3C%2Fem%3E)%20feared%20States%20who%20would%20deprive%20us%20of%20information%2C%20Aldous%20Huxley%20(%3Cem%3EBrave%20New%20World%3C%2Fem%3E)%20those%20that%20would%20overwhelm%20us%20with%20so%20much%20that%20truth%20would%20be%20drowned%20out.%20The%2020th%20century%20fascist%20dictatorships%20used%20Orwellian%20tools%2C%20their%2021st%20century%20counterparts%20Huxleyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20frontrunner%20of%20these%20trends%2C%20or%20at%20least%20that%20part%20of%20the%20country%20north%20of%20the%20Vindhyas.%20One%20is%20led%20to%20wonder%20how%20this%20far%20right%20turn%20could%20have%20occurred%20in%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20India%20whose%20foundational%20ideology%20is%20Gandhian-Nehruvian.%20This%20stems%20at%20least%20partly%20from%20the%20smugness%20of%20old%20elites%20in%20brushing%20aside%20subaltern%20concerns.%20Similar%20questions%20were%20asked%20by%20historians%20of%20the%20far%20right%20turn%20in%20Germany%20in%20the%201930s.%20Why%20was%20there%20so%20little%20resistance%20and%20outrage%20in%20civil%20society.%20It%20is%20important%20however%20to%20look%20beyond%20the%20surface%20to%20the%20currents%20in%20motion%20beneath%20it.%20Despite%20the%20overt%20secular%20democratic%20framework%2C%20soft%20Hindutva%20has%20been%20the%20dominant%20ideology%20in%20large%20parts%20of%20northern%20India%20since%20the%20days%20of%20the%20national%20movement.%20This%20has%20now%20morphed%20into%20hard%20Hindutva.%20Those%20who%20were%20socialised%20into%20soft%20Hindutva%20are%20perhaps%20not%20sufficiently%20motivated%20or%20outraged%20to%20oppose%20hard%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20India%20is%20only%20a%20microcosm%20of%20what%20is%20occurring%20globally.%20Old%20wine%20in%20new%20bottles%20is%20the%20zeitgeist%20of%20our%20current%20times.%20Look%20about%20you.%20Turkey%20and%20Eastern%20Europe%20have%20been%20veering%20rightwards%20for%20a%20while.%20Both%20China%20and%20Russia%20have%20taken%20a%20sharp%20nationalist%20right-wing%20turn%20under%20Xi%20and%20Putin.%20The%20prospects%20for%20the%20return%20of%20Trump%20are%20strong.%20The%20far%20right%20coasted%20to%20victory%20in%20Italy%2C%20and%20more%20recently%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20both%20core%20countries%20of%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20the%20bastion%20of%20liberalism%20and%20democracy.%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%20in%20France%20and%20the%20AfD%20in%20Germany%20are%20on%20the%20rampage%20in%20what%20is%20the%20heart%20of%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Parliament%2C%20CAG%2C%20EC%3A%20More%20Pillars%20Crumble%20as%20Modi%20Tightens%20Hold%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-cag-ec-more-pillars-crumble-as-modi-tightens-hold%5C%22%3EParliament%2C%20CAG%2C%20EC%3A%20More%20Pillars%20Crumble%20as%20Modi%20Tightens%20Hold%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20of%20my%20generation%20brought%20up%20on%20a%20diet%20of%20individual%20rights%2C%20democracy%2C%20secularism%20and%20universalist%20beliefs%20will%20just%20have%20to%20sit%20out%20the%20decline%20of%20populist%20and%20charismatic%20right-wing%20authorities.%20They%20have%20nothing%20new%20to%20contribute%20to%20human%20progress%20over%20the%20long%20run%2C%20as%20these%20are%20counterrevolutionary%20attempts%20to%20put%20the%20clock%20back.%20This%20too%20shall%20pass%2C%20like%20the%201930s%20did.%20But%20the%20latter%20exited%20after%20a%20huge%20catastrophe%20that%20underlay%20the%20long%20peace%20and%20strengthened%20institutions%20of%20the%20postwar%20era.%20Can%20we%20see%20off%20the%20new%20bottle%20without%20major%20catastrophe%3F%20I%20normally%20send%20out%20a%20forward-looking%20message%20of%20hope%20to%20friends%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20each%20year.%20I%20struggled%20to%20pen%20something%20hopeful%20that%20could%20also%20be%20straight%20from%20the%20heart.%20The%20best%20I%20could%20come%20up%20with%20was%20my%20translation%20of%20a%20poem%20by%20the%20Urdu%20poet%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Year%20what%20about%20you%20is%20new%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhat%20of%20all%20this%20festivity%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20the%20self-same%20daylight%20I%20view%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20self-same%20stars%20at%20night%20there%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20looks%20like%20yesterday%20to%20me%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnNeither%20the%20skies%20above%20have%20changed%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnNor%20the%20ground%20below%20that%20I%20see%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnJust%20some%20numbers%20are%20rearranged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20this%20year%20be%20like%20those%20before%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20with%20it%20the%20same%20twelve%20months%20bring%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20you%20are%20new%20then%20show%20me%20more%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20new%20dawn%2C%20new%20awakening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20come%20and%20go%20these%20eyes%20have%20seen%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnNew%20Year%20take%20me%20where%20they%20have%20never%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlok%20Sheel%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant%20and%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703996580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupload