t.%20But%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20was%20able%20to%20bypass%20the%20congestion%20by%20taking%20a%20private%20jet%20to%20Denver%20from%20Teterboro%20Airport%20in%20New%20Jersey%20that%20day%2C%20prompting%20an%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20a%20private%20jet%20was%20the%20wrong%20decision%20because%20it%20was%20insensitive%20to%20our%20customers%20who%20were%20waiting%20to%20get%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement.%20%26quot%3BI%20sincerely%20apologize%20to%20our%20customers%20and%20our%20team%20members%20who%20have%20been%20working%20around-the-clock%20for%20several%20days%20-%20often%20through%20severe%20weather%20-%20to%20take%20care%20of%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20parting%20with%20that%20paycheck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank%20CEO%20Greg%20Becker%20refused%20to%20commit%20to%20giving%20up%20his%20%2410%20million%20pay%20after%20the%20bank%20collapsed%20in%20March.%20Lawmakers%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20bank%20failures%20cost%20the%20government's%20bedrock%20deposit%20insurance%20fund%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20which%20will%20have%20to%20be%20replenished%20by%20other%20lenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20took%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20criticism%2C%20Becker%20told%20the%20Senate%20Banking%20Committee%20that%20unprecedented%20events%2C%20interest-rate%20hikes%20and%20negative%20social%20media%20coverage%20rather%20than%20mismanagement%20were%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20the%20firm's%20demise.%20Becker%20said%20he'd%20work%20with%20regulators%20to%20review%20compensation%2C%20but%20wouldn't%20pledge%20to%20give%20anything%20back%20despite%20being%20pressed%20repeatedly%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20HBO%20troll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECasey%20Bloys%2C%20CEO%20of%20HBO%20and%20Max%20content%2C%20apologized%20for%20using%20fake%20X%20accounts%20to%20troll%20TV%20critics%20who%20gave%20bad%20reviews%20to%20the%20network's%20shows%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%20According%20to%20the%20Times%2C%20Bloys%20said%20his%20passion%20for%20his%20company's%20programming%20-%20and%20too%20much%20time%20on%20social%20media%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20-%20led%20him%20to%20do%20it%20and%20he%20concluded%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%2C%20very%20dumb%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20posts%2C%20first%20reported%20in%20Rolling%20Stone%2C%20were%20surfaced%20in%20a%20wrongful%20termination%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20a%20former%20HBO%20employee.%20Bloys%20apologized%20to%20the%20journalists%20named%20in%20the%20article%20and%20said%20he%20now%20sends%20direct%20messages%20to%20those%20he%20disagrees%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPre-pink%20slip%20digital%20detox%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20CEO%20Marc%20Benioff%20says%20he%20took%20a%2010-day%20trip%20to%20French%20Polynesia%20for%20a%20so-called%20digital%20detox%20ahead%20of%20the%20company's%20mass%20layoff%20of%20about%208%2C000%20staff.%20A%20digital%20detox%20is%20when%20someone%20forgoes%20phones%20or%20computers%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20to%20feel%20more%20present%20and%20less%20dependent%20on%20technology%20and%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20employees%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Benioff%20said%20the%20company%20hired%20too%20many%20workers%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20he%20took%20responsibility%20for.%20But%20Benioff%20also%20appeared%20tone-deaf%2C%20arriving%20late%20to%20a%20meeting%20the%20day%20after%20the%20layoff%2C%20joking%2C%20%26quot%3Bdid%20I%20miss%20something%3F%26quot%3B%20Some%20pointed%20out%20the%20irony%20of%20the%20sudden%20job%20cuts%20next%20to%20Benioff's%20frequent%20characterization%20of%20the%20company%20as%20an%20Ohana%2C%20a%20Hawaiian%20term%20for%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703992200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-1