mands%20or%20your%20vehicle's%20on-screen%20infotainment%20system%2C%20as%20shown%20here.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FRobert%20Galbraith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20CarPlay%20is%20an%20iPhone%20mirroring%20system%20for%20vehicles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20your%20car%20comes%20with%20Apple%20CarPlay%2C%20you%20can%20connect%20your%20phone%20to%20the%20system%20to%20do%20various%20tasks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENavigation%2C%20music%2C%20and%20hands-free%20texting%20are%20among%20the%20functions%20that%20CarPlay%20can%20enable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20Apple%20CarPlay%20is%20just%20a%20way%20to%20stream%20music%20while%20you%20drive%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20know%20the%20half%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranted%2C%20CarPlay%20does%20make%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20stream%20music%20from%20your%20smartphone%2C%20but%20there%20are%20several%20useful%20feature%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-iphone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%3C%2Fa%3E%20mirroring%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20CarPlay%20lets%20you%20interact%20with%20your%20phone%20via%20voice%20commands%20or%20your%20vehicle's%20on-screen%20infotainment%20system%20to%20do%20things%20like%20dictate%20text%20messages%2C%20get%20turn-by-turn%20directions%2C%20make%20phone%20calls%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20rolled%20out%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202014%20at%20the%20Geneva%20International%20Motor%20Show%2C%20per%20Apple's%20Newsroom%2C%20CarPlay%20is%20now%20a%20standard%20feature%20in%20more%20than%20800%20models%20of%20vehicles%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20car%20is%20one%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20use%20an%20iPhone%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20this%20integrative%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20connect%20to%20Apple%20CarPlay%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConnecting%20to%20CarPlay%20could%20not%20be%20much%20easier.%20First%2C%20make%20sure%20your%20car%20is%20running%20(not%20driving!)%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmarter-siri-ai-messages-apple-iphone-ipad-mac-homepod-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESiri%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20enabled%20on%20your%20iPhone.%20Then%2C%20if%20you%20are%20using%20a%20USB-to-lighting%20or%20USB-C%20cable%2C%20simply%20connect%20your%20phone%20to%20the%20vehicle%20via%20wire.%20Your%20device%20will%20automatically%20connect%20to%20CarPlay%20in%20any%20automobile%20equipped%20with%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wired%20connection%20will%20also%20enable%20your%20phone%20to%20connect%20wirelessly%20in%20cars%20where%20that%20is%20an%20option.%20You%20will%20get%20an%20alert%20on%20your%20phone%20asking%20permission%20to%20grant%20the%20wireless%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setup%20process%20is%20slightly%20different%20in%20vehicles%20where%20only%20a%20wireless%20CarPlay%20connection%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20use%20CarPlay%20wirelessly%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20connect%20to%20CarPlay%20wirelessly%2C%20ensure%20your%20car%20is%20on%20and%20Siri%20is%20enabled%20on%20your%20iPhone.%20Put%20your%20car's%20infotainment%2Faudio%20system%20into%20Bluetooth%20mode%2C%20then%20hold%20down%20the%20voice%20command%20button.%20On%20your%20phone%2C%20open%20Settings%2C%20tap%20WiFi%2C%20and%20then%20tap%20the%20CarPlay%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20back%20in%20Settings%2C%20go%20to%20General%2C%20tap%20CarPlay%2C%20and%20select%20your%20vehicle.%20Your%20phone%20will%20now%20be%20connected%20and%20reconnect%20each%20time%20you%20turn%20on%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20use%20Apple%20CarPlay%20without%20USB%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20CarPlay%20can%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20used%20wirelessly%20in%20some%20vehicles.%20In%20other%20cases%2C%20you%20can%20use%20CarPlay%20wirelessly%20after%20you've%20initially%20connected%20your%20phone%20to%20your%20car's%20CarPlay%20with%20a%20USB%20cable%2C%20received%20an%20alert%20on%20your%20phone%20to%20grant%20wireless%20permission%2C%20and%20accepted%20the%20wireless%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20apps%20are%20compatible%20with%20Apple%20CarPlay%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20CarPlay%20works%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-announces-new-apple-music-streaming-app-2015-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pandora%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-music%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20many%20more%20music%20apps.%20You%20can%20also%20manage%20and%20listen%20to%20audiobooks%20and%20podcasts%20with%20CarPlay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavigation%20apps%20are%20another%20big%20functionality%20to%20control%20via%20CarPlay%2C%20which%20is%20compatible%20with%20Apple%20Maps%2C%20Google%20Maps%2C%20Waze%2C%20TomTom%2C%20and%20others.%20Using%20these%20apps%2C%20you%20can%20get%20turn-by-turn%20directions%20powered%20by%20your%20phone%20but%20fed%20through%20your%20car's%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarPlay%20also%20works%20with%20messenger%20apps%2C%20including%20iMessage%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-whatsapp-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Snapchat%2C%20Telegram%2C%20and%20others.%20You%20can%20use%20CarPlay%20to%20dictate%20messages%20or%20have%20them%20read%20via%20Siri%20so%20you%20can%20text%20hands-free%20and%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20even%20manage%20your%20Calendar%20app%2C%20Zoom%20meetings%2C%20news%20apps%2C%20email%2C%20and%20your%20phone's%20Settings%20app%2C%20all%20using%20voice%20commands%20or%20the%20touchscreen%20or%20steering%20wheel%20interface%20native%20to%20your%20vehicle's%20infotainment%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20a%20monthly%20fee%20for%20Apple%20CarPlay%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20CarPlay%20is%20free.%20There%20is%20no%20initial%20purchase%2C%20nor%20are%20there%20any%20ongoing%20fees%20to%20be%20paid.%20CarPlay%20is%20a%20native%20feature%20on%20many%20current%20and%20recently%20released%20cars%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20an%20upgrade%20or%20an%20aftermarket%20addition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20you%20can%20pay%20for%20an%20infotainment%20system%20with%20CarPlay%20installed%20in%20an%20older%20vehicle%20that%20does%20not%20have%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20disadvantages%20of%20Apple%20CarPlay%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20way%20of%20thinking%2C%20there%20are%20few%20downsides%20because%20Apple%20CarPlay%20is%20optional.%20You%20can%20always%20choose%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20native%20features%20of%20your%20vehicle%20instead%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20used%20CarPlay%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20worth%20noting%20that%20CarPlay%20does%20not%20work%20with%20every%20app%2C%20so%20some%20actions%20may%20be%20limited%20while%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20you%20use%20it%2C%20CarPlay%20may%20require%20some%20engagement%20with%20a%20screen%2C%20and%20that%20means%20taking%20your%20eyes%20off%20the%20road%20%E2%80%94%20never%20a%20good%20thing%20when%20you%20are%20driving.%20But%20if%20you%20exclusively%20use%20voice%20commands%20when%20connected%20to%20CarPlay%2C%20this%20is%20not%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20there%20is%20no%20significant%20customization%20allowed%20with%20CarPlay.%20The%20apps%20and%20control%20functions%20must%20be%20used%20as%20they%20populate%20on%20your%20car's%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-carplay%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703961301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ec1deab6f