rt%20against%20the%20proposed%20demolition%20of%20the%20structure%20due%20to%20alleged%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20the%20area%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Abdul%20Aziz%20challenged%20a%20December%2024%20public%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20(NDMC)%20seeking%20objections%20and%20suggestions%20from%20the%20general%20public%20by%20January%201%20regarding%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20January%208%20after%20the%20NDMC%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20said%20to%20the%20court%20that%20nothing%20would%20happen%20in%20the%20meantime%20as%20a%20final%20call%20on%20the%20action%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20Heritage%20Conservation%20Committee%20(HCC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeven%20deaths%20and%20743%20new%20COVID-19%20cases%20in%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20recorded%20743%20new%20COVID-19%20cases%20along%20with%20seven%20deaths%2C%20according%20to%20data%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mohfw.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3EMinistry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20active%20cases%20has%20however%20recorded%20a%20decrease%20to%203%2C997%20on%20Saturday%20from%204%2C091%20recorded%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20comes%20with%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20JN.1%20cases.%20At%20least%20162%20cases%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20JN.1%20have%20been%20detected%20in%20India%20so%20far%2C%20with%20the%20highest%2083%20sequences%20coming%20from%20Kerala%2C%20according%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20genome%20sequencing%20consortium%20INSACOG%2C%20reported%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-covid-19-new-cases-9088516%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EB