with%20ULFA%20Had%20Lost%20its%20Worth%20Even%20Before%20It%20Was%20Inked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30190015%2FEffect-48.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Historic!%C2%A0Thus%20far%2C%20all%20agreements%20that%20the%20Centre%20(be%20it%20of%20any%20party)%20has%20signed%20with%20an%20armed%20outfit%20in%20Northeast%20India%20have%20been%20termed%20either%20by%20the%20signatories%2C%20or%20their%20political%20backers%2C%20no%20less%20than%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20till%20they%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20nowhere%20near%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2029%2C%20signing%20the%20agreement%20with%20the%20Arabinda%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA)%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20quite%20predictably%20termed%20it%20too%20as%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20only%20time%20can%20tell%20how%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20is%20this%20agreement%3B%20also%2C%20if%20it%20is%20more%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20than%20the%20Assam%20accord%20delivered%20by%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201985%2C%20which%20this%20new%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20peace%20accord%E2%80%99%20signed%20by%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20even%20make%20a%20mention%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20Assam%2C%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20one%20has%20seen%20three%20%E2%80%98peace%20accords%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Bodoland%E2%80%99%20area%20itself%2C%20signed%20with%20various%20Union%20governments%20held%20by%20the%20two%20national%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Each%20was%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20till%20it%20was%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20one%2C%20signed%20with%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202020%2C%20was%20also%20termed%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20by%20Shah.%20However%2C%20the%20All%20Bodo%20Students%20Union%20(ABSU)%20president%20Dipen%20Boro%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Famit-shah-historic-bodo-peace-accord-sign-assam-1640584-2020-01-27%5C%22%3Estated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kokrajhar%20on%20December%2029%20that%20the%20agreement%20has%20not%20been%20%E2%80%9Cimplemented%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit%20by%20the%20state%20and%20central%20(Modi)%20government%E2%80%9D%20and%20if%20not%20done%20soon%2C%20the%20outfit%20vows%20to%20start%20a%20%E2%80%98democratic%20movement%E2%80%99.%20The%20ability%20of%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20ministry%20to%20prove%20that%20the%202020%20agreement%20was%20indeed%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20is%20already%20under%20a%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20history%20has%20shown%20over%20and%20again%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20crafting%20one%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20peace%20agreement%20or%20the%20other%20with%20groups%20spearheading%20armed%20movements%20across%20the%20Northeast%20(remember%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20Naga%20Framework%20Agreement%20from%202015%3F)%2C%20time%20is%2C%20perhaps%2C%20not%20only%20to%20reckon%20the%20transient%20nature%20of%20these%20pacts%20but%20to%20cognise%20the%20need%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20%E2%80%93%20once%20and%20for%20all%20%E2%80%93%20to%20this%20litany.%20Simply%20because%20these%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreements%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20nothing%20but%20hollow%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20efficacy%20in%20profiting%20the%20public%20in%20general%20and%20the%20community%20it%20is%20intended%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fulfa-faction-signs-peace-accord-with-centre-political-gimmick-says-opposition-in-assam%5C%22%3EULFA%20Faction%20Signs%20%E2%80%98Peace%20Accord%E2%80%99%20with%20Centre%3B%20%E2%80%98Political%20Gimmick%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20Opposition%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20must%20the%20Assamese%20public%20learn%20from%20the%20December%2029%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20moment%20scripted%20within%20closed%20doors%20in%20their%20name%3F%20Importantly%2C%20what%20must%20they%20do%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20march%20of%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreements%20with%20some%20angry%20group%20or%20the%20other%20by%20%3Cem%3ENotun%20Dilli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(New%20Delhi)%20ends%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20is%20simple%3B%20history%20must%20be%20the%20teacher%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeneficiaries%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98peace%20accord%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20to%20the%20prescriptive%20part%2C%20it%20is%20helpful%20though%20to%20hold%20up%20who%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20this%20latest%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20there%20are%20clearly%20three%20direct%20beneficiaries.%20One%20is%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20ULFA.%20Since%202008%2C%20its%20cadres%20have%20been%20waiting%20in%20designated%20camps%20(set%20up%20by%20the%20government)%20for%20their%20leaders%20to%20pull%20off%20an%20%E2%80%98honourable%E2%80%99%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre.%20So%20that%2C%20they%20can%20not%20only%20get%20a%20means%20of%20livelihood%20but%20also%20integrate%20back%20into%20society.%20However%2C%20with%20nothing%20in%20sight%2C%20waiting%20for%20years%20together%2C%20several%20of%20them%20had%20begun%20deserting%20those%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20with%20Arabinda%20Rajkhowa%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA).%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40AmitShah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20among%20those%20disillusioned%20with%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20had%20begun%20looking%20for%20employment%20on%20their%20own%2C%20some%20others%20had%20gone%20back%20to%20the%20jungles%20to%20join%20the%20anti-talks%20faction%20of%20ULFA%20run%20by%20Paresh%20Barua%20from%20Myanmar.%20What%20needs%20highlighting%20here%20is%20that%20most%20of%20that%20lot%20are%20the%20sons%20and%20daughters%20of%20Assamese%20peasants.%20This%20upheaval%20within%20Assamese%20peasantry%20is%20huge%20considering%20Assam%20is%20an%20agricultural%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20advent%20in%20North%20Block%20in%202014%2C%20the%20interlocutor%20appointed%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20talks%20with%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20had%20changed.%20It%20meant%20the%20talks%20had%20to%20begin%20afresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20that%20new%20interlocutor%20was%20shifted%20out%20too.%20These%20changes%20have%20certainly%20slowed%20down%20the%20process.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20the%20initial%20euphoria%20within%20the%20Assamese%20public%20and%20the%20intellectuals%20about%20the%20likelihood%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20Assam%20Accord%20(no%20more%20historic%20by%20then)%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20another%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20pact%20through%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20ULFA%20began%20to%20lose%20steam.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20December%2029%20agreement%20with%20New%20Delhi%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20its%20worth%20is%20already%20diminished.%20Nobody%20in%20Assam%20expected%20it%20to%20be%20truly%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slowdown%20of%20the%20peace%20process%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20to%20tire%20out%20those%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20table%20because%20it%20ended%20up%20benefitting%20the%20Centre.%20It%20was%20exhausting%20for%20the%20ULFA%20leaders%20to%20wait%20endlessly%20for%20Godot%20to%20arrive.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20which%20has%20at%20least%20a%20semblance%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98honourable%E2%80%99%20exit%20for%20them.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20with%20their%20dwindling%20bargaining%20chips%2C%20the%20ULFA%20leaders%20needed%20this%20agreement%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20more%20than%20New%20Delhi%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inherent%20pressure%20on%20them%20to%20conclude%20a%20process%20that%20they%20had%20started%20with%20the%20Centre%20in%202011%20ensured%20that%20their%20stakes%20to%20sign%20on%20the%20dotted%20line%20were%20certainly%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20Centre.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Assamese%20public%20looked%20on%2C%20with%20mixed%20feelings.%20Whether%20to%20expect%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%2C%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20no%20government%20(read%20party)%20will%20show%20any%20generosity%20to%20a%20militant%20group%20unless%20it%20looks%20at%20it%20as%20a%20milcher.%20It%20is%20particularly%20true%20with%20the%20Modi-era%20BJP.%20The%20timing%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20must%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20prime%20mover%20for%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Here%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20most%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20of%20the%20state%20are%20in%20Upper%20Assam%2C%20the%20Assamese%20heartland.%20It%20is%20also%20in%20Upper%20Assam%20that%20the%20efficacy%20of%20ULFA%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98sentinel%E2%80%99%20of%20Assamese%20interests%20has%20not%20died%20down%20fully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20have%20publicly%20stated%20that%20they%20have%20no%20political%20ambitions%2C%20what%20stops%20them%20from%20publicly%20endorsing%20the%20party%20that%20delivered%20the%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20crucial%202024%20elections%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20can%20project%20the%20Assamese%20public%20that%20they%20brought%20home%20an%20%E2%80%98honourable%E2%80%99%20agreement%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20rocket%20science%20that%20with%20the%20entire%20South%20India%20now%20virtually%20BJP-mukt%2C%20the%20party%20desperately%20needs%20to%20shore%20up%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20as%20possible%20from%20other%20corners%20of%20the%20country.%20If%20reviving%20the%20frenzy%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20in%20West%20Bengal%20before%20the%202024%20polls%20can%20help%20dress%20up%20BJP%20as%20always%20working%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20a%20large%20swathe%20of%20Bengalis%2C%20in%20Assam%20too%2C%20an%20accord%20with%20the%20pro-talks%20faction%20of%20ULFA%20should%20be%20able%20to%20project%20to%20the%20majority%20Assamese%20community%20that%20the%20party%20is%20indeed%20pro-%3Cem%3EKhilonjia%3C%2Fem%3E%20(indigenous).%20The%20BJP%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20another%20direct%20beneficiary%20of%20this%20timely%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20is%20the%20third%20direct%20beneficiary.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20he%20has%20to%20prove%20his%20worth%20to%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20his%20new%20party%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20hot%20seat.%20The%20chief%20minister%20can%20do%20that%20only%20by%20delivering%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20126%20seats%20of%20Assam%20during%20an%20assembly%20election%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20during%20a%20parliamentary%20poll.%20In%20the%202024%20campaign%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20his%20voice%20about%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20having%20arrived%20in%20Assam%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Northeast%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98Modi%20sarkar%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20loudest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20must%20the%20common%20Assamese%20do%20to%20ensure%20that%20such%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreements%20never%20take%20place%20in%20their%20name%3B%20their%20%3Cem%3Ekhilonjia%3C%2Fem%3E%20sentiments%20can%20never%20be%20misused%20by%20one%20political%20group%20or%20the%20other%20in%20future%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20is%20already%20lit%20if%20lessons%20from%20history%20are%20learnt.%20The%20answer%20clearly%20is%20not%20in%20taking%20up%20guns.%20Let%20history%20be%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20guns%20have%20only%20brought%20bodies%20home%2C%20often%20to%20the%20poorest%20families.%20The%20gun%20culture%20in%20Assam%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Northeast%20has%20only%20helped%20produce%20a%20set%20of%20self-serving%20political%20leaders%20by%20misusing%20community%20sentiments%3B%20have%20served%20only%20some%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%20desperation%20to%20win%20an%20election%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protracted%20ULFA%20movement%20generated%20a%20bunch%20of%20Assamese%20youth%20to%20go%20for%20easy%20money%20through%20extortions%20and%20helped%20create%20a%20batch%20of%20selfish%20Assamese%20businessmen%20who%20have%20little%20interest%20in%20building%20any%20public%20good%20apart%20but%20only%20to%20fill%20their%20personal%20%3Cem%3Ebhoral%20%3C%2Fem%3E(coffer).%20This%20should%2C%20by%20now%2C%20be%20an%20eye%20opener%20for%20the%20community%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Assamese%20youth%20and%20society%20in%20general%20must%20then%20focus%20on%2C%20and%20stridently%20so%2C%20is%20to%20gun%20only%20for%20self-reliance.%20Till%20the%20land%20you%20own%3B%20there%20is%20no%20shame%20in%20it.%20It%20can%20not%20only%20make%20you%20self-sufficient%20but%20also%20help%20generate%20employment%20in%20rural%20areas.%20It%20may%20help%20turn%20the%20trend%20of%20Assamese%20villages%20increasingly%20becoming%20the%20cesspool%20of%20cheap%20labour%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20and%20more%20youth%20must%20start%20believing%20in%20their%20business%20acumen%3B%20allow%20their%20competitive%20nature%20to%20flower.%20They%20must%20strive%20to%20know%20their%20history%2C%20not%20tailored%20by%20any%20political%20force%20to%20push%20their%20agenda%20but%20those%20by%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20greats%3B%20they%20have%20left%20enough%20material%20for%20the%20generations%20to%20know%20who%20is%20truly%20an%20Assamese.%20The%20strive%20for%20%E2%80%98independence%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20community%2C%20and%20the%20state%20in%20turn%2C%20must%20be%20in%20ensuring%20that%20individual%20hard%20work%20contributes%20to%20creating%20a%20collective%20good.%20This%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20must%20prod%20us%20towards%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20several%20success%20stories%20of%20entrepreneurship%20already%20in%20the%20state%2C%20a%20silent%20revolution%20of%20sorts%20has%20begun.%20The%20focus%20must%20be%20to%20add%20to%20it%20a%20swarm%20of%20more%20such%20stories.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20a%20community%20can%20have%20political%20heft%20only%20when%20it%20has%20economic%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20aim%20for%20the%20community%20must%20be%20to%20embrace%20excellence.%20An%20important%20component%20of%20it%20is%2C%20but%2C%20to%20produce%20leaders%20with%20integrity%20and%20spine%2C%20in%20every%20field.%20It%20also%20means%20discarding%20those%20who%20are%20purely%20self-serving%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20political%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20clutch%20of%20resolve%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20delivering%20greater%20profit%20to%20the%20Assamese%20public%20in%20general%20than%20banking%20on%20an%20elusive%20saviour%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20with%20tall%20promises%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20realise%20later%20that%20it%20was%20not%20quite%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703944990000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30190015%2FEffect-48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-historic-peace-accord-with-ulfa-lost-its-worth-even-before-it-was-inked%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20agreement%20is%20just%20another%20addition%20to%20a%20litany%20of%20previous%20'historic'%20agreements%20signed%20with%20militant%20groups%20in%20the%20region.%20Only%20time%20will%20tell%20whether%20this%20'historic'%20accord%20stands%20out%20from%20others%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20hollow.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-historic-peace-accord-with-ulfa-lost-its-worth-even-before-it-was-inked%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reflections%20on%20a%20Disturbing%20Year%20Gone%20By.%20And%20the%20Challenges%20That%20Lie%20Ahead.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20ends%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20doom.%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20Palestine.%20It%20is%20about%20our%20own%20country%2C%20India.%20The%20images%20of%20a%20heavily-garlanded%20Brijbhushan%20Singh%20with%20a%20victory%20sign%20celebrating%20the%20win%20of%20his%20proxy%20in%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20post%20of%20president%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20juxtaposed%20with%20the%20image%20of%20the%20decorated%20Olympian%20wrestler%20Sakshi%20Malik%20crying%20and%20hanging%20up%20her%20shoes%20before%20the%20media%20define%20the%20state%20and%20mood%20of%20India%20in%20our%20times.%20Malik%2C%20along%20with%20some%20other%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20had%20levelled%20charges%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20molestation%20against%20Singh%20and%20had%20been%20fighting%20against%20him%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Singh%2C%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%2C%20clearly%20has%20the%20full%20support%20of%20his%20party%20and%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20a%20sad%20reflection%20on%20us%20all%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20thinks%20there%20will%20be%20no%20political%20price%20to%20pay%20if%20it%20ignores%20the%20cries%20of%20these%20women%20athletes%20who%20have%20risen%20from%20the%20dusty%20lanes%20of%20villages%20and%20done%20the%20country%20proud%20by%20winning%20in%20international%20competitions.%20The%20country%20saw%20a%20stormy%20agitation%20after%20a%20woman%20was%20raped%20in%20Delhi%20only%2011%20years%20back.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20mass%20movement%20of%20sympathy%20or%20solidarity%20for%20them.%20Our%20campuses%20remained%20calm%20even%20when%20the%20images%20of%20women%20wrestlers%20being%20dragged%20away%20from%20their%20protest%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20went%20viral.%20It%20did%20not%20cause%20a%20ripple%20in%20the%20consciousness%20of%20the%20people%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20treated%20them%20with%20contempt%2C%20smelled%20conspiracy%20in%20their%20charges%20and%20agitation%2C%20and%20mocked%20them.%20The%20Delhi%20police%2C%20which%20had%20arrested%20the%20fact-checker%20journalist%20Md%20Zubair%20on%20laughably%20flimsy%20charges%20under%20POCSO%2C%20dragged%20its%20feet%2C%20and%20even%20after%20concluding%20that%20Singh%20did%20commit%20sexual%20offences%2C%20not%20once%20but%20multiple%20times%2C%20decided%20to%20let%20him%20remain%20free.%20There%20was%20no%20media%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20days%20we%20also%20saw%20the%20mass%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20belonging%20to%20the%20opposition%20parties%20from%20both%20houses.%20Yet%2C%20the%20news%20of%20crucial%20bills%20being%20passed%20in%20the%20near%20total%20absence%20of%20the%20opposition%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20disturbed%20the%20media%20and%2C%20through%20them%2C%20the%20wider%20public.%20Everything%20is%20being%20done%20with%20the%20force%20of%20numbers.%20Where%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20complaint%3F%20The%20opposition%20MPs%20are%20asked%20to%20behave%20and%20respect%20the%20majority.%20The%20media%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20warning%20the%20people%20of%20the%20serious%20consequences%20these%20new%20laws%20are%20going%20to%20have%20on%20all%20aspects%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20has%20mildly%20complained%20about%20the%20breach%20of%20parliamentary%20processes%20but%20has%20got%20busy%20with%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20supposedly%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20discussing%20the%20list%20of%20invitees%20and%20who%20is%20being%20honoured%20with%20the%20invitation%20and%20who%20has%20been%20left%20out.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20your%20reputation%20depends%20on%20your%20place%20in%20the%20invitee%20list.%20We%20have%20heard%20about%20some%20prominent%20opposition%20members%20being%20invited.%20But%20we%20do%20not%20expect%20them%20to%20reject%20the%20invite%20by%20pointing%20to%20the%20criminal%20way%20in%20which%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98legal%E2%80%99%20usurpation%20of%20its%20land%20for%20the%20temple%2C%20and%20why%20it%20is%20unholy%20to%20build%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%20of%20what%20the%20Supreme%20court%20called%20an%20%E2%80%98egregious%20crime%E2%80%99%20committed%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20upholding%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20refusing%20to%20rule%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20turning%20the%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20territories%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20once%20again%20shown%20its%20willingness%20to%20legally%20legitimize%20acts%20of%20majoritarianism.%20It%20has%2C%20by%20doing%20this%2C%20pursued%20its%20logic%20of%20%E2%80%98what%20is%20done%20is%20done%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98what%20the%20government%20wills%2C%20will%20happen.%E2%80%99%20This%20is%20in%20keeping%20with%20its%202019%20Babri%20Mosque%20judgment%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20land%20to%20those%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20of%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%202023%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20ruling%20allowing%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98archaeological%20survey%E2%80%99%2C%20thus%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20changing%20the%20character%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20making%20the%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20redundant.%20The%20constitutional%20scheme%2C%20designed%20to%20keep%20the%20nation%20together%2C%20is%20being%20systematically%20dismantled%2C%20and%20the%20apex%20court%20is%20facilitating%20it%2C%20even%20as%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%20keeps%20giving%20weekend%20speeches%20waxing%20eloquent%20about%20great%20constitutional%20and%20humanist%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20judiciary%20led%20by%20the%20incumbent%20CJI%2C%20like%20his%20predecessors%2C%20is%20breathtaking.%20While%20speaking%20for%20individual%20liberty%20endlessly%2C%20the%20CJI%2C%20as%20master%20of%20the%20roster%2C%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20bail%20petitions%20of%20people%20arrested%20(clearly%20because%20of%20their%20politics)%20end%20up%20before%20judges%20known%20for%20their%20aversion%20to%20the%20primacy%20of%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20judiciary%20refusing%20to%20perform%20its%20role%20as%20constitutional%20watchdog%2C%20it%20seems%20impossible%20to%20stop%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Efrom%20reconfiguring%20the%20constitutional%20frame.%20The%20party%20has%20numbers%20and%20is%20getting%20no%20pushback%20from%20the%20elites%20of%20India.%20The%20corporate%20world%20adopted%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20its%20man%20way%20back%20in%202007%20%E2%80%93%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ein%20return%20for%20which%20he%20has%20allowed%20the%2C%20to%20capture%20all%20the%20national%20and%20natural%20resources%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20endless%20violence%20and%20hateful%20propaganda%2C%20society%20has%20been%20torn%20apart%20so%20badly%20that%20the%20Indian%20nation%20as%20a%20shared%20zone%20of%20sensibilities%20is%20coming%20under%20severe%20strain.%20One%20can%20see%20this%20starkly%20in%20Manipur.%20Meitei%20majoritarian%20violence%20with%20state%20patronage%20has%20wrecked%20the%20state%20and%20divided%20it%20into%20two%20parts%20which%20now%20cannot%20sit%20face%20to%20face.%20Kukis%20have%20lost%20all%20hope%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20valley%2C%20and%20Meiteis%20cannot%20go%20to%20the%20hills.%20Kukis%20have%20managed%20to%20safeguard%20themselves%20as%20they%20have%20hills%20to%20fortify%20themselves%20in%20and%20also%20resources%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20violence%20they%20have%20faced.%20But%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20other%20minorities%20do%20not%20have%20this%20%E2%80%98advantage%E2%80%99%20to%20save%20themselves%20from%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20minorities%20or%20any%20socially%20vulnerable%20section%20of%20the%20population%20cannot%20expect%20protection%20from%20the%20state%20apparatus%2C%20including%20the%20judiciary.%20Civil%20society%20has%20been%20effectively%20disabled.%20The%20media%20has%20done%20its%20best%20to%20convince%20the%20people%20that%20members%20of%20civil%20society%20are%20their%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20ebbs%20with%20Umar%20Khalid%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%20Khalid%20Saifi%20and%20Gulfisha%20Fatima%20completing%20three%20years%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20jails%20and%20Shoma%20Sen%2C%20Mahesh%20Raut%2C%20Hany%20Babu%2C%20and%20others%20completing%20five%20years%20in%20the%20jails%20of%20Maharashtra.%20They%20are%20forgotten%20people%20who%20fought%20for%20lost%20causes.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20indifference%20to%20their%20plight%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20do%20not%20relate%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%20now%20to%20analyse%20and%20our%20job%20is%20merely%20to%20record%20and%20describe%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Indian%20dream.%20But%20this%20is%20luxury%20people%20in%20India%20cannot%20afford.%20Sitting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20a%20gloomy%20winter%20day%20I%20feel%20helpless.%20But%20then%20I%20get%20calls%20from%20a%20farmer%20friend%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20He%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20From%20a%20state%20which%20is%20most%20oppressive%20for%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20practise%20democracy.%20For%20Muslims%20even%20more%20so.%20Here%20is%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20who%20believes%20that%202024%20is%20still%20open.%20We%20can%20still%20turn%20the%20tide%20and%20recover%20our%20democracy.%20He%20has%20a%20plan%20and%20also%20friends%20and%20he%20wants%20political%20parties%20to%20listen%20to%20him.%20Or%20my%20friends%20from%20a%20youth%20group%20in%20Pune%20who%20have%20been%20training%20workers%20of%20different%20political%20parties%20and%20reminding%20them%20that%20the%20fight%20is%20for%20larger%20ideas%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20gains%20that%20power%20brings.%20And%20they%20feel%20encouraged%20that%20party%20workers%20listen.%20And%20then%20our%20friend%20Alok%20Shukla%20from%20Chhattisgarh%20informs%20us%20that%20the%20adivasis%20of%20Hasdeo%20Aranya%20are%20still%20fighting%20against%20mining%20and%20their%20dispossession%2C%20even%20after%20knowing%20that%20the%20state%20has%20a%20more%20brutal%20government%20in%20power%20now.%20The%20parents%20and%20partners%20of%20those%20in%20prison%20still%20keep%20reminding%20the%20courts%20of%20their%20duty.%20I%20see%20the%20images%20of%20calm%20Muslim%20women%20carrying%20Palestinian%20flags%20which%20are%20snatched%20by%20the%20policemen%20and%20torn.%20She%20looks%20at%20him%20disapprovingly%20but%20keeps%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20sign%20off%2C%20my%20doorbell%20rings.%20Here%20is%20my%20young%20journalist%20friend%20from%20Punjab.%20He%20is%20on%20way%20to%20Chandigarh%20after%20spending%20the%20week%20with%20the%20wrestlers%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20others.%20He%20is%20upbeat.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20you%20think%20it%20is%20a%20victory%20that%20these%20wrestlers%20who%20could%20not%20think%20beyond%20awards%20only%20a%20year%20back%20now%20stand%20upright%20before%20a%20mighty%20state%20knowing%20well%20what%20they%20are%20up%20against%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20asks.%20%C2%A0%20I%20cannot%20but%20agree.%20The%20fight%20is%20still%20left%20in%20us.%20It%20is%20not%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703944225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Freflections-on-a-disturbing-year-gone-by-and-the-challenges-that-lie-ahead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20endless%20violence%20and%20hateful%20propaganda%2C%20the%20Indian%20nation%20as%20a%20shared%20zone%20of%20sensibilities%20is%20coming%20under%20severe%20strain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Freflections-on-a-disturbing-year-gone-by-and-the-challenges-that-lie-ahead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imran%20Khan%20rejected%20as%20candidate%20in%20Pakistan%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703943660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-imran-khan-pakistan_6407546.jpg%3F20231230140613%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fimran-khan-rejected-as-candidate-in-pakistans