fHR%20founder%20Sunita%20Vishwanath.%20And%20exposed%20her%20Soros%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20are%20we%20accused%20of.%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20dig%3F%20But%20we%20dig.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaPo%20deliberately%20omitted%20the%20critical%20part%E2%80%93%20we%20dug%20into%20HfHR%20BECAUSE%20of%20its%20IAMC%20connect%20%26amp%3B%20FOUND%20Soros!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(16%2Fn)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXpPxvYp0zl%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXpPxvYp0zl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20DisInfo%20Lab%20(%40DisinfoLab)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDisinfoLab%2Fstatus%2F1734430424989147223%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20find%20this%20response%20hugely%20problematic%20at%20several%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20George%20Soros%E2%80%99%20Open%20Society%20Foundation%20(OSF)%20had%20years%20ago%20funded%20Women%20for%20Afghan%20Women%20(WAW)%2C%20cofounded%20by%20Sunita%2C%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20public%20record%20and%20needed%20no%20%E2%80%9Cdigging.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWAW%20was%20dedicated%20to%20education%20of%20girls%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20a%20society%20stymied%20by%20conservative%20views%20on%20women%20and%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20Taliban.%20She%20was%20recognised%20by%20President%20Obama%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Champion%20of%20Change%E2%80%99%20for%20her%20courageous%20work%20in%20Afghanistan%20as%20well%20as%20for%20her%20work%20in%20Sadhana%3A%20Coalition%20of%20Progressive%20Hindus%2C%20which%20she%20had%20cofounded.%20When%20the%20Taliban%20came%20back%20to%20power%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1123502451548398%5C%22%3Eshe%20risked%20travelling%20to%20Afghanistan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20plead%20with%20the%20rulers%20to%20allow%20girls%20to%20go%20back%20to%20school.%20Unfortunately%2C%20despite%20impassioned%20pleas%20from%20her%20and%20others%2C%20Afghan%20girls%20remain%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20OSF%20chose%20to%20fund%20such%20an%20important%20cause%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20most%20funders%20were%20afraid%20of%20getting%20involved%20in%20a%20war%20zone%2C%20should%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20celebration%2C%20not%20boorish%20attacks.%20As%20I%20see%20it%2C%20a%20bit%20more%20honest%20%E2%80%9Cdigging%E2%80%9D%20by%20Disinfo%20Lab%20would%20have%20shown%20that%20the%20OSF%20has%20a%20record%20of%20supporting%20pro-democracy%20initiatives%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20One%20among%20them%20that%20I%20am%20personally%20familiar%20with%20is%20Malaysiakini%2C%20the%20only%20news%20portal%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Malaysia%20that%20does%20not%20toe%20the%20party%20line%20and%20is%20unafraid%20to%20defend%20the%20rights%20of%20minority%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDisinfo%20Lab%20may%20have%20very%20well%20succeeded%20in%20convincing%20itself%20and%20Modi%20acolytes%20that%20Soros%20is%20bent%20on%20destroying%20democracies.%20But%20OSF%E2%80%99s%20long%20record%20of%20giving%20tells%20a%20very%20different%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20convincing%20Modi%20acolytes%20that%20the%20IAMC%20has%20terror%20links%20must%20have%20been%20quite%20easy%20given%20that%20those%20obsessed%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20ISI%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Disinfo%20Lab%E2%80%99s%20founder%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20Col.%20Dibya%20Satpathy%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20willing%20to%20believe%20just%20about%20anything%20negative%20about%20a%20Muslim%20organisation%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%20A%20very%20low%20bar%20indeed%20for%20those%20whose%20very%20foundations%20are%20built%20on%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%98joins%E2%80%99%C2%A0Disinfo%20Lab%E2%80%99s%20conspiracy%20theory%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20and%20when%20did%20Rahul%20suddenly%20become%20a%20part%20of%20Disinfo%20Lab%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Sunita-IAMC-Soros%E2%80%99%20fake%20conspiracy%20theory%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20best%20as%20I%20can%20tell%2C%20it%20was%20triggered%20by%20a%20photograph%20of%20Sunita%20sitting%20close%20to%20Rahul%20during%20his%20appearance%20at%20a%20Washington%20think%20tank%20event.%20Even%20though%20there%20were%20more%20than%2060%20people%20in%20the%20room%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20cell%20mischievously%20broadcast%20the%20selective%20photo%20of%20Sunita%20and%20Rahul%20as%20evidence%20of%20a%20meeting%20between%20them%20to%20conspire%20against%20India.%20That%20very%20photograph%20was%20brandished%20later%20on%20Indian%20national%20TV%20by%20Irani%20as%20proof%20of%20a%20Rahul-Soros-Sunita%20conspiracy!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20here%20in%20a%20nutshell%20is%20Disinfo%20Lab%E2%80%99s%20theory%3A%20OSF%20funding%20for%20Sunita%E2%80%99s%20Afghan%20women%E2%80%99s%20organisation%20%E2%80%9Cproves%E2%80%9D%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclose%20associate%E2%80%9D%20of%20George%20Soros.%20HfHR%E2%80%99s%20partnership%20with%20IAMC%20%E2%80%9Cproves%E2%80%9D%20that%20Sunita%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20connections%20with%20anti-India%20Islamist%20forces.%E2%80%9D%20A%20photograph%20of%20her%20sitting%20next%20to%20Rahul%20in%20a%20large%20meeting%20%E2%80%9Cproves%E2%80%9D%20that%20she%20was%20conspiring%20with%20him%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdestroy%E2%80%9D%20India!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20astonishing%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20uncritically%20broadcast%20such%20a%20malevolent%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20has%20put%20Sunita%2C%20me%2C%20and%20many%20others%20in%20harm%E2%80%99s%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDubious%20roles%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELong%20before%20the%20attacks%20on%20HfHR%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20proxies%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20the%20diaspora%20have%20been%20actively%20harassing%20those%20of%20us%20who%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20We%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20incessant%20social%20media%20attacks%2C%20disrupted%20meetings%2C%20attacks%20in%20our%20academic%20conferences%2C%20leading%20to%20even%20death%20and%20rape%20threats.%20Some%20of%20these%20proxies%20have%20also%20been%20amplifying%20and%20supporting%20the%20work%20of%20DL.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20American%20Foundation%20(HAF)%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20such%20efforts.%20Its%20highlight%20was%20a%20SLAPP%20lawsuit%20filed%20against%20Sunita%2C%20me%2C%20and%20three%20others%2C%20who%20were%20accused%20of%20conspiring%20to%20defame%20HAF%2C%20for%20merely%20%E2%80%93%20and%20independently%20%E2%80%93%20opining%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fsangh-parivars-us-funds-trail%2Farticle35117629.ece%5C%22%3Eemergency%20COVID-19%20funding%20received%20by%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20lawsuit%20was%20thrown%20out%20by%20the%20judge%20as%20lacking%20any%20merit%2C%20but%20not%20before%20the%20HAF%20had%20spent%20several%20hundred%20thousand%20dollars%20in%20legal%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20HAF%20was%20also%20the%20first%20group%20to%20come%20to%20Disinfo%20Lab%E2%80%99s%20defence%20following%20the%20%3Cem%3EWaPo%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%2C%20confirming%20for%20me%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20proxies%20in%20the%20diaspora%20are%20every%20bit%20as%20guilty%20as%20the%20BJP%20itself%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20shut%20down%20dissent%20overseas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20next%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20strongly%20believe%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20done%20itself%20a%20great%20disservice%20by%20signalling%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20any%20lengths%20to%20silence%20anyone%20in%20the%20diaspora%20who%E2%80%99s%20unafraid%20to%20speak%20the%20ugly%20truth%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20authoritarian%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20HfHR%20is%20not%20deterred%20in%20the%20least%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20and%20make%20a%20case%20for%20saving%20Indian%20democracy.%20Our%20support%20base%20is%20already%20expanding%20since%20the%20Irani%20attack%2C%20and%20our%20young%20team%20of%20warriors%20is%20energized%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20welcome%20the%20new%20year%20by%20rededicating%20ourselves%20to%20the%20task%20of%20speaking%20up%20for%20the%20oppressed%20all%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20our%20work%20will%20speak%20for%20itself%20and%20we%20will%20reach%20ever%20wider%20audiences%20in%20America%20and%20will%20in%20turn%20make%20the%20Biden%20administration%20see%20the%20light%20about%20its%20faulty%20India%20policy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hard%20truth%20is%20that%20Modi%2C%20aided%20by%20propaganda%20groups%20like%20the%20Disinfo%20Lab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhither-parliamentary-democracy-2821446%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edo%20not%20need%20any%20external%20enemies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20destroy%20Indian%20democracy.%20They%20are%20doing%20a%20pretty%20good%20job%20of%20it%20already.%20As%20we%20enter%20the%20new%20year%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20earnest%20hope%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20Hindus%20in%20India%20will%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20imminent%20danger%20of%20the%20Modi%20rule%20to%20India%20and%20to%20Hinduism%20itself%20before%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20late.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERaju%20Rajagopal%20is%20with%20Hindus%20for%20Human%20Rights.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17