tent%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FVVPAT-machine-PIB.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20first%20joint%20protest%20of%20the%2028-party%20Opposition%20Alliance%20INDIA%2C%20on%20December%2022%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20called%20for%20unity%2C%20saying%20democracy%20is%20under%20threat%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20leaders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Funite-to-save-democracy-says-mallikarjun-kharge-at-india-bloc-s-protest-101703238843871.html%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20opposition%20parties%20came%20together%20to%20form%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20because%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Shah%20are%20trying%20to%20destroy%20democracy%20and%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20meeting%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20earlier%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20resolved%20to%20fight%20authoritarianism%20with%20full%20might%20saying%20that%20democracy%20and%20constitution%20are%20under%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20meeting%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20adopted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Findia-bloc-passes-resolution-on-suspension-of-mps-evms-operation-2478038-2023-12-19%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%3A%20%E2%80%9CINDIA%20parties%20reiterate%20that%20there%20are%20many%20doubts%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVMs.%20These%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20many%20experts%20and%20professionals%20as%20well.%20There%20is%20widespread%20demand%20for%20a%20return%20to%20the%20ballot%20paper%20system%E2%80%A6%20INDIA%20parties%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98happy%E2%80%99%20if%20there%20was%20a%20return%20to%20voting%20through%20ballot%20paper%E2%80%A6%20If%20ECI%20has%20any%20reservations%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20and%20desirable%20to%20have%20a%20hybrid%20ballot%20paper-EVM%20system%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%E2%80%A6%20It%20suggested%20that%20instead%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20falling%20in%20the%20box%2C%20it%20should%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20voter%20who%20shall%20then%20place%20it%20in%20a%20separate%20ballot%20box%20after%20having%20verified%20his%20or%20her%20choice.%20100%25%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20then%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20solace%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbetter%20late%20than%20never!%E2%80%9D%20But%2C%20with%20parliament%20election%20only%20weeks%20away%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20follow-up%20action%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resolution%20is%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fecisveep-eci-must-implement-its-constitutional-mandate-to-conduct-free-and-fair-election%5C%22%3Eadoption%20of%20the%20public%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20initiated%20by%20civil%20society%20on%20August%2024%2C%20signed%20by%20over%207%2C000%20voters%20and%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ECI%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEVM%2FVVPAT%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20essential%20%E2%80%98Democracy%20Principles%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20that%20each%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20verify%20that%20her%20vote%20is%20cast-as-intended%2C%20recorded-as-cast%20and%20counted-as-recorded.%20Though%20the%20ECI%20has%20arranged%20for%20all%20EVMs%20to%20be%20accompanied%20with%20VVPAT-device%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Voter-Verifiable%20Paper%20Trail%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20level%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98bioscope%E2%80%99%20which%20shows%20up%20a%20tiny%20%E2%80%98paper%20slip%E2%80%99%20for%20seven%20seconds%20which%20then%20vanishes%20and%20is%20NOT%20counted%E2%80%A6.%20The%20VVPAT%20system%20should%20therefore%20be%20re-calibrated%20to%20be%20fully%20voter-verifiable.%20A%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20in%20her%20hand%20and%20cast%20it%20in%20a%20chip-free%20ballot%20box%20for%20the%20vote%20to%20be%20valid.%20These%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20fully%20counted%20for%20all%20constituencies%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%20For%20this%20purpose%2C%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20larger%20in%20size%20and%20must%20be%20printed%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20can%20be%20preserved%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20was%20initiated%20because%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20intention%20and%20capacity%20to%20hold%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20as%20per%20its%20constitutional%20mandate%20has%20been%20fading%20fast.%20It%20reached%20a%20nadir%20recently%20when%20the%20Commission%20filed%20a%20counter-affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20containing%20these%20assertions%20which%20are%20alien%20to%20the%20very%20concept%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EECI%20is%20under%20no%20obligation%20to%20cross-verify%20EVMs%20with%20VVPATs%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20VVPAT%20is%20only%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20voter%20can%20verify%20that%20her%20vote%20has%20been%20cast%20as%20intended%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20no%20fundamental%20right%20in%20voters%20to%20verify%20that%20their%20votes%20have%20been%20recorded%20as%20cast%20and%20counted%20as%20recorded%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAny%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20VVPATs%20to%20be%20cross-verified%20will%20pose%20an%20administrative%20challenge%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E100%25%20verification%20of%20VVPAT%20is%20a%20regressive%20step%20and%20takes%20the%20country%20back%20to%20manual%20counting%20of%20ballots%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarlier%20ballot%20counting%20systems%20used%20to%20take%20between%201%20to%206%20days.%20It%20will%20take%20more%20time%20if%20VVPATs%20are%20counted%20and%20recounted%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEVMs%20cannot%20be%20tampered%20with.%20They%20have%20a%20one-time%20programmable%20chip.%20Cannot%20be%20hacked.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECI%20seems%20to%20be%20under%20the%20archaic%20and%20colonial%20belief%20that%20elections%20are%20favours%20bestowed%20on%20the%20people%20of%20India%20and%20not%20instruments%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20sovereignty%20from%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20The%20People%E2%80%9D%20to%20our%20elected%20representatives%20to%20run%20the%20government%20on%20our%20behalf.%20This%20is%20a%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20building%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PIB_INDIA.%20November%205%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20disturbing%20is%20that%20ECI%20has%20been%20falsely%20claiming%20that%20the%20EVM%20(BU-VVPAT-CU)%20units%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20standalone%20machines%20having%20one-time%20programmable%20chips.%E2%80%9D%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20name%20and%20symbols%20of%20the%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20to%20EVM%20using%20an%20external%20device%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20and%20finalisation%20of%20the%20candidate%20list.%C2%A0%20ECI%20Manual%20itself%20states%20at%208.4.2%20that%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20engineers%20are%20to%20use%20a%20device%20called%20Symbol%20Loading%20Unit%20(SLU)%20to%20electronically%20upload%20these%20details%20to%20the%20VVPAT.%20The%20same%20Manual%20in%208.4.4%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20devices%20need%20not%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20strong%20room%20along%20with%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20and%20are%20to%20be%20released%20to%20the%20engineers%20immediately%20after%20the%20poll%20thus%20making%20them%20outside%20of%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20Returning%20Officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wired%20connection%20of%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20to%20an%20external%20device%20not%20maintained%20within%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20Returning%20Officers%2FDistrict%20Election%20Officers%20after%20election%20is%20announced%2C%20candidate%20sequence%20is%20firmed%20up%2C%20and%20second%20randomisation%20and%20booth%20allotment%20of%20EVMs%20finalised%20makes%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20practices%20in%20conducting%20elections%20extremely%20suspect.%20This%20has%20exposed%20the%20voting%20and%20counting%20to%20insider%2Foutsider%20manipulation%20with%20ECI%20being%20a%20party%20to%20it.%20This%20cannot%20be%20countenanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-indias-elections-free-and-fair%5C%22%3EAre%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%20Free%20and%20Fair%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20actual%20voting%20process%2C%20a%20voter%20presses%20the%20ballot%20button%20opposite%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%20on%20the%20EVM%20and%20will%20hear%20a%20beep%20sound.%20A%20slip%20appears%20in%20the%20transparent%20window%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine.%20The%20slip%20with%20the%20Candidate%20serial%20No.%2C%20Name%20and%20Symbol%20are%20visible%20for%207%20seconds%20before%20they%20drop%20in%20the%20sealed%20VVPAT%20box.%20The%20slip%20is%20too%20small%20to%20handle%2C%20printed%20on%20thermal%20paper%20and%20evaporates%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks%2Fmonths.%20This%20is%20suspect%20and%20non-transparent.%20A%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20in%20his%2Fher%20hand%20and%20cast%20it%20in%20a%20chip-free%20ballot%20box%20for%20the%20vote%20to%20be%20valid.%C2%A0%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20larger%20in%20size%20and%20must%20be%20printed%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20cannot%20be%20altered%20and%20can%20be%20preserved%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20votes%20recorded%20in%20the%20EVM%20is%20counted%20by%20pressing%20the%20appropriate%20button%20marked%20%E2%80%9CResult%E2%80%9D%20provided%20in%20the%20Control%20Unit%20whereby%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20polled%20by%20each%20candidate%20are%20displayed%20in%20respect%20of%20each%20such%20candidate%20on%20the%20display%20panel%20provided%20for%20the%20purpose%20in%20the%20unit.%20Corresponding%20entries%20made%20in%20a%20result%20sheet%20in%20Form%2020%20and%20the%20particulars%20so%20entered%20in%20the%20result%20sheet%20is%20announced.%20Rule%2056D(4)(b)%20of%20the%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20(Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202013%20provides%20for%20the%20primacy%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20count%20over%20the%20electronic%20tally%20of%20ballots%20cast%20and%20calculated%20on%20the%20EVMs.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20that%20should%20be%20fully%20counted%20for%20all%20constituencies%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20any%20candidate%2C%20or%20in%20his%20absence%2C%20his%20election%20agent%20or%20any%20of%20his%20counting%20agents%20may%20apply%20in%20writing%20to%20the%20returning%20officer%20to%20count%20the%20printed%20paper%20slips%20in%20the%20drop%20box%20of%20the%20printer%20in%20respect%20of%20any%20polling%20station%20or%20polling%20stations.%20On%20such%20application%20being%20made%2C%20the%20returning%20officer%20shall%20decide%20the%20matter%20and%20may%20allow%20the%20application%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%20or%20may%20reject%20in%20whole%2C%20if%20it%20appears%20to%20him%20to%20be%20frivolous%20or%20unreasonable.%20This%20is%20a%20highly%20arbitrary%20and%20undemocratic%20process%20which%20can%20be%20brazenly%20misused%2Fabused%20by%20election%20officials%20under%20political%20pressure%20as%20has%20been%20happening.%20The%20correct%20process%20is%20to%20count%20only%20VVPAT%20slips.%20If%20needed%2C%20results%20of%20the%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20could%20be%20cross-verified%20with%20the%20electronic%20tallies%20of%20the%20EVMs%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%20In%20case%20of%20any%20mismatch%2C%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20the%20final%20result.%20Forms%2017A%20(Register%20of%20Electors)%20and%20Forms%2017C%20(Account%20of%20votes%20recorded)%20must%20be%20tallied%20with%20the%20manual%20count%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20before%20the%20declaration%20of%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20essential%20aspects%20of%20Electoral%20Democracy%2C%20which%20are%20well%20within%20the%20remit%20of%20the%20ECI%20and%20are%20doable%20within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20are%20the%20demands%20contained%20in%20the%20public%20petition%20to%20the%20ECI%20which%20the%20Commission%20refuses%20even%20to%20acknowledge%20obviously%20under%20directions%20from%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20who%20are%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20current%20flawed%20and%20undemocratic%20system.%20In%20the%20event%20is%20it%20not%20the%20duty%20and%20responsibility%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20take%20up%20this%20issue%20vigorously%20to%20ensure%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20with%20integrity%3F%20But%20so%20far%20INDIA%20Block%20has%20failed%20in%20their%20duty%20while%20in%20our%20neighbouring%20small%20countries-Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh-EVMs%20have%20been%20discarded%20because%20of%20joint%20action%20by%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20bloc%20should%20realise%20that%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Celection%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%E2%80%9D%20have%20become%20synonymous.%20As%20of%20now%20the%20only%20way%20to%20choose%20our%20representatives%20to%20govern%20ourselves%20is%20through%20the%20electoral%20process.%20%E2%80%9CResolving%20to%20fight%20authoritarianism%20with%20full%20might%20to%20defend%20Democracy%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20noble%20thing%20to%20do.%20But%20it%20should%20start%20with%20ensuring%20the%20fairness%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20Block%20to%20defend%20India%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20would%20become%20a%20question%20mark.%20And%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%20this%20could%20be%20disastrous!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703938034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FVVPAT-machine-PIB.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commission-must-recognise-vvpat-paper-trail-is-central-to-infusing-trust-in-evms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20demand%20for%20this%20in%20a%20resolution%20was%20initiated%20by%20civil%20society%20in%20August%20because%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20intention%20and%20capacity%20to%20hold%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20as%20per%20its%20constitutional%20mandate%20has%20been%20fading%20fast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commission-must-recognise-vvpat-paper-trail-is-central-to-infusing-trust-in-evms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20Returns%20as%20JD(U)%20Chief%3A%20Move%20to%20Strengthen%20INDIA%20or%20Possible%20Re-Entry%20to%20the%20NDA%20Fold%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165226%2FEffect-47.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20back%20as%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20president%20replacing%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20alias%20Lallan%20Singh.%20According%20to%20the%20party%20leaders%2C%20Singh%20requested%20Nitish%20to%20take%20over%20the%20mantle%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20as%20he%20wants%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20Munger%20parliamentary%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20of%20guard%20took%20place%20at%20the%20two-day%20national%20executive%20and%20national%20council%20meeting%20of%20the%20JDU%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CLallan%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20he%20had%20become%20the%20party%20chief%20at%20the%20order%20of%20Nitish%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20requested%20that%20he%20would%20be%20busier%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20and%20requested%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20take%20over%20as%20the%20party%20president%20which%20the%20latter%20accepted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bihar%20finance%20minister%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsiders%20in%20the%20party%20revealed%20that%20the%20JDU%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20affairs%20would%20work%20with%20more%20vigour%20and%20coherence%20to%20strengthen%20the%20campaign%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20at%20the%20two-day%20meeting%20deliberated%20on%20the%20caste%20survey%3B%20increasing%20job%20quota%20for%20the%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20to%2065%25%3B%20employing%20over%201.25%20school%20teachers%3B%20and%20according%20%E2%80%98government%20servant%E2%80%99%20status%20to%204%2C40%2C000%20contract%20teachers%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20party%20focused%20on%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Nitish%20government%20and%20dropped%20hints%20to%20pit%20the%20%E2%80%98Bihar%20model%E2%80%99%2C%20built%20on%20real%20issues%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20campaign%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20cadres%20are%20in%20a%20jubilant%20mood%20over%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20comeback%20as%20the%20president.%20They%20ruled%20out%20any%20possibility%20of%20factionalism%20surfacing%20in%20the%20party%20with%20Nitish%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20underlining%20that%20he%20is%20an%20acceptable%20leader%20for%20everyone%20in%20the%20party.%20Lallan%20who%20accompanied%20Nitish%20in%20the%20car%20to%20the%20JDU%20office%20ahead%20of%20demitting%20his%20position%20too%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20JDU%20was%20united%2C%20is%20united%2C%20and%20will%20remain%20united.%E2%80%9D%20He%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20media%20for%20%E2%80%9Cplaying%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20building%20a%20false%20narrative%20around%20the%20JDU%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20George%20Fernandes-led%20Samata%20Party%20merged%20into%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20of%20Sharad%20Yadav-led%20faction%20in%202003%20and%20became%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20of%20which%20Sharad%20was%20the%20founding%20president.%20Nitish%20took%20over%20as%20its%20president%20in%202016%20and%20continued%20till%20he%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20Ram%20Chandra%20Prasad%20(RCP)%20Singh%20in%202020.%20Lallan%20Singh%20replaced%20RCP%20who%20was%20axed%20from%20the%20party%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELallan%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20quit%20his%20position%20in%20favour%20of%20Nitish%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20electoral%20reality%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20The%20Munger%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20known%20for%20the%20predominance%20of%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmis%2C%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs)%2C%20and%20minorities.%20The%20baton%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20a%20benefactor%20of%20the%20EBCs%20and%20Mahadalits%20%E2%80%93%20is%20likely%20to%20smoothen%20the%20rough%20edges%20in%20the%20relationship%20of%20various%20caste%20groups%20and%20unite%20them%20behind%20Lallan%2C%20an%20upper%20caste%20Bhumihar%20in%20the%202024%20polls.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20could%20weaken%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20rope%20in%20the%20non-Yadav%20EBCs%20who%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20Munger%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWild%20speculations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20about%20Lallan%E2%80%99s%20exit%20as%20the%20party%20chief%20ahead%20of%20the%20JDU%E2%80%99s%20meet%20set%20in%20motion%20wild%20speculations%20with%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20predicting%20that%20Nitish%20might%20be%20replacing%20Lallan%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfacilitate%E2%80%9D%20his%20%E2%80%9Cre-entry%E2%80%9D%20into%20the%20NDA.%20Several%20channels%20said%20that%20Lallan%20had%20got%20%E2%80%9Cclose%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20discomfiture%20of%20Nitish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20rung%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20asserted%20that%20Nitish%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpeeved%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20not%20making%20him%20convenor%20and%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20%E2%80%9Cways%E2%80%9D%20to%20rejoin%20the%20NDA.%20To%20the%20chagrin%20of%20the%20JDU%20leadership%2C%20such%20rumours%20have%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20over%20a%20week%20despite%20all%20the%20top%20party%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20K.%20C.%20Tyagi%2C%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20and%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Choudhary%20%E2%80%93%20repeatedly%20denying%20these%20rumours%20and%20demonstrating%20the%20JDU%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunwavering%E2%80%9D%20commitment%20to%20strengthening%20the%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%2C%20who%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20uniting%20various%20non-BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Delhi%20chief%20ministers%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvin%20Kejriwal%20respectively%2C%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20INDIA%2C%20clarified%20on%20December%2025%20that%20he%20does%20not%20have%20any%20personal%20ambition%20and%20only%20wanted%20all%20the%20parties%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20fight%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20saying%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20post%20for%20myself.%20What%20I%20want%20is%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20sharing%20of%20seats%20among%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitish%20said%20after%20paying%20tribute%20to%20former%20prime%20minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20on%20his%20birth%20anniversary%20on%20December%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20a%20section%20of%20channels%20reported%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstories%E2%80%9D%20of%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cannoyance%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20for%20not%20making%20him%20a%20convenor%3B%20he%20was%20feeling%20%E2%80%9Cinsulted%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cway%20out%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165410%2FGCiCMDnaoAAy1y2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165410%2FGCiCMDnaoAAy1y2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165410%2FGCiCMDnaoAAy1y2-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165410%2FGCiCMDnaoAAy1y2-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENitish%20Kumar%20and%20other%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leaders%20at%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20executive%20meeting%20in%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40LalanSingh_1%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDubious%20feedback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20operatives%20allegedly%20owing%20allegiance%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20cells%20flooded%20the%20internet%20with%20the%20news%20of%20%E2%80%9Cturmoil%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20JDU%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esirphutaual%3C%2Fem%3E%20(quarrel)%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20linking%20it%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccrisis%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20JDU.%20Koiri%20leader%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%20who%20is%20with%20the%20BJP%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20try%20for%20Nitish%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20honourable%20entry%20into%20the%20NDA%20if%20he%20disassociated%20himself%20from%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20ruling%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20comprising%20RJD%2C%20JDU%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20revealed%20that%20the%20talks%20of%20sharing%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20among%20them%20in%20Bihar%20were%20in%20the%20final%20stages.%20But%20reacting%20to%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20JDU%20on%20Friday%2C%20several%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Union%20ministers%20Ashwini%20Choubey%20and%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doors%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%20were%20shut.%20His%20days%20as%20the%20CM%20are%20numbered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20confidant%20of%20Nitish%20reacted%20as%20such%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20has%20Nitish%20knocked%20at%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20door%3F%20The%20BJP%20is%20resorting%20to%20dubious%20tricks%20to%20damage%20Nitish%20%3Cem%3Eji%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3Es%20image.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealistically%2C%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20that%20is%20in%20troubled%20waters%20in%20Bihar%20after%20Nitish%20deserted%20it%20in%20August%202022%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%20It%20is%20an%20electorally%20proven%20reality%20that%20the%20RJD%20enjoys%20impregnable%20hold%20on%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%20who%20together%20constitute%20over%2031%25%20of%20the%20voters%2C%20and%20Nitish%20enjoys%20the%20same%20over%20the%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs)%20who%20are%2036.01%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20report.%20Nitish%20has%20increased%20his%20hold%20over%20this%20population%20by%20raising%20their%20reservation%20in%20government%20jobs%20from%2018%25%20to%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20hard%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20OBC%20and%20EBC%E2%80%99s%20social%20base%20empowered%20and%20nursed%20well%2C%20earlier%20by%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20now%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20The%20BJP%20is%2C%20apparently%20playing%20all%20the%20tricks%20to%20foment%20differences%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Mahagathbandhan%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20weaken%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703935863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165226%2FEffect-47.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-returns-as-jdu-chief-move-to-strengthen-india-or-possible-re-entry-into-the-nda-fold%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20multiple%20theories%20going%20around%20over%20the%20change%20of%20guard%20in%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%20While%20some%20say%20the%20move%20is%20to%20bring%20coherence%20to%20the%20campaign%20of%20INDIA%2C%20others%20say%20the%20development%20should%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20light%20of%20Nitish%20being%20'peeved'%20at%20INDIA%20bloc%20for%20not%20making%20him%20the%20convenor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-returns-as-jdu-chief-move-to-strengthen-india-or-possible-re-entry-into-the-nda-fold%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22titl