Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20regarding%20pending%20cases%20has%20been%20disclosed%20by%20replies%20received%20to%20appeals%20filed%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%2C%20said%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2029%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Soren%20right%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprdjharkhand%2Fstatus%2F1211287224005869574%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprdjharkhand%2Fstatus%2F1211287224005869574%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704003291869000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3j-rVqc82fALGEMexM9eft%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Pathalgadi%20cases%2C%20it%20was%20met%20with%20widespread%20appreciation%20and%20support.%20The%20earlier%20Jharkhand%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Das%2C%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Pathalgadi%C2%A0movement%20and%20responded%20with%20severe%20violence%20and%20repression.%20It%20had%20filed%20several%20cases%20against%20the%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20movement%20and%20also%20several%20Adivasi%20traditional%20heads%20of%20the%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20filed%20several%20cases%20against%20about%20200%20named%20accused%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20unnamed%20people%20under%20charges%20that%20included%20abetment%2C%20obstruction%20to%20public%20servants%20discharging%20their%20duty%2C%20creation%20of%20public%20nuisance%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20and%20even%20sedition.%20As%20many%20as%2028%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20related%20to%20the%20P%3Cspan%3Eathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20movement%20were%20spread%20across%20Khunti%20(21)%2C%20Saraikela-Kharsawan%20(5)%2C%20and%20West%20Singhbhum%20(2)%20districts%20were%20registered%20by%20the%20Raghubar%20Das%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20Soren%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20raised%20during%20the%20%3Cspan%3EPathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20widespread%20violation%20of%20special%20laws%20and%20provisions%20for%20Adivasis%20(PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20etc.)%2C%20marginalisation%20of%20Adivasi%20worldview%2C%20exploitation%20of%20Adivasis%20by%20the%20police%2C%20administration%2C%20and%20non-Adivasis%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20Soren%20government%20to%20immediately%20withdraw%20all%20five%20pending%20%3Cspan%3EPathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20cases%2C%20initiate%20action%20against%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20Khunti%2C%20and%20award%20compensation%20to%20victims.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20calling%20for%20the%20strict%20implementation%20of%20special%20laws%20and%20provisions%20for%20Adivasis%20such%20as%20PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20and%20so%20on%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703930056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F22171455%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-22-at-3.48.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pending%20cases%20name%20Stan%20Swamy%20along%20with%2020%20other%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%20associated%20with%20the%20movement.%C2%A0On%2029%20December%202019%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20soon%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20had%20announced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Pathalgadi%20cases.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22