C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F5-9-magnitude-earthquake-shakes-indonesias-aceh-province-no-casualties-reported%2Farticleshow%2F106398578.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106398578.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20strong%20undersea%20earthquake%20shook%20Indonesia's%20Aceh%20province%2C%20but%20caused%20no%20serious%20damage%20or%20casualties.%20The%20magnitude%205.9%20earthquake%20occurred%20east%20of%20Sinabang%20at%20a%20depth%20of%2010%20kilometers.%20Indonesia's%20Meteorology%2C%20Climatology%20and%20Geophysical%20Agency%20warned%20of%20possible%20aftershocks%20but%20stated%20there%20was%20no%20tsunami%20threat.%20Indonesia%20is%20prone%20to%20earthquakes%20and%20volcanic%20eruptions%20due%20to%20its%20location%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BRing%20of%20Fire.%26quot%3B%20Recent%20deadly%20earthquakes%20in%20West%20Java%20and%20Sulawesi%20have%20caused%20significant%20loss%20of%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F5-9-magnitude-earthquake-shakes-indonesias-aceh-province-no-casualties-reported%2Farticleshow%2F106398578.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F5-9-magnitude-earthquake-shakes-indonesias-aceh-province-no-casualties-reported%2Famp_articleshow%2F106398578.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F5-9-magnitude-earthquake-shakes-indonesias-aceh-province-no-casualties-reported%2Famp_articleshow%2F106398578.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ULFA%20Faction%20Signs%20'Peace%20Accord'%20with%20Centre%3B%20'Political%20Gimmick%2C'%20Says%20Opposition%20in%20Assam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20several%20years%20of%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%2C%20the%20pro-talks%20faction%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA)%20has%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20to%20formally%20shun%20violence%20and%20disband%20the%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%2C%20termed%20%E2%80%98peace%20accord%E2%80%99%20by%20both%20sides%2C%20was%20signed%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2029%2C%20by%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20with%20the%20head%20of%20this%20faction%20of%20the%20ULFA%2C%20Arabinda%20Rajkhowa%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20home%20secretary%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Bhalla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20terms%2C%20clauses%2C%20and%20promises%20of%20the%20agreement%20have%20not%20been%20made%20public%20yet%2C%20a%20press%20meet%20held%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Rajkhowa-faction%20after%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20agreement%20in%20Delhi%20said%2097%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20126%20assembly%20seats%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98reserved%E2%80%99%20for%20indigenous%20people%20but%20the%20parameters%20of%20declaring%20who%20is%20indigenous%20would%20be%20in%20accordance%20to%20the%20broad%20guidelines%20and%20methodology%20adopted%20for%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20state%20in%202023.%20The%20ULFA%20leaders%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20MHA%20has%20told%20them%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20consider%E2%80%9D%20recommending%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20guidelines%20for%20future%20delimitation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investment%20of%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%2C%20staggered%20through%20years%2C%20is%20also%20a%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20promise%20under%20the%20agreement%2C%20besides%20declaring%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20annual%20floods%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98national%20priority%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20agreement%2C%20the%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20soon%20to%20look%20into%20reservations%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%3B%20also%20relook%20at%20the%20updated%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRCs)%20and%20make%20voter%20enumeration%20process%20stricter%3B%20and%20land%20evicted%20by%20encroachers%20would%20to%20be%20distributed%20among%20landless%20indigenous%20people.%20A%20committee%20would%20look%20into%20the%20issue%20of%20sick%20tea%20gardens%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outfit%E2%80%99s%20founding%20leaders%20including%20Anup%20Chetia%20and%20Sasadhar%20Choudhury%20present%20at%20the%20press%20meet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fassam%2Fcentre-assam-government-sign-peace-accord-with-pro-talks-faction-of-ulfa-2829198%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20would%20disband%20the%20outfit%3B%20their%20cadres%20would%20vacate%20the%20designated%20camps%20being%20run%20by%20the%20government%20since%202008%3B%20their%20arms%20kept%20in%20joint%20custody%20with%20the%20government%20since%20would%20be%20surrendered%20to%20the%20authorities%20too.%20They%20also%20said%20they%20have%20no%20political%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20they%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20agreed%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20state%20till%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20is%20hearing%20a%20set%20of%20petitions%20on%20it%2C%20gives%20its%20final%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20both%20Shah%20and%20Sarma%20termed%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98golden%20day%E2%80%99%20for%20Assam.%20Shah%20gave%20all%20credit%20to%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cvision%20for%20a%20prosperous%2C%20peaceful%20and%20developed%20Northeast%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20turn%2C%20Modi%2C%20on%20X%2C%20said%20the%20agreement%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20peace%20and%20development%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20peace%20and%20development.%20This%20agreement%2C%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20lasting%20progress%20in%20Assam.%20I%20commend%20the%20efforts%20of%20all%20involved%20in%20this%20landmark%20achievement.%20Together%2C%20we%20move%20towards%20a%20future%20of%20unity%2C%20growth%2C%20and%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY8sqPr1KPJ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY8sqPr1KPJ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1740771156603625798%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20in%20Assam%20have%2C%20however%2C%20termed%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20gimmick%E2%80%9D%20before%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20pact%20does%20not%20look%20like%20an%20agreement%20between%20a%20sovereignty%20seeking%20group%20and%20the%20government.%20Many%20of%20the%20clauses%20mentioned%20in%20the%20agreement%20are%20just%20some%20routine%20duties%20of%20any%20elected%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20Debabrata%20Saikia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F12%2F29%2Fcal25-as-ulfa-accord-oppn.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20PTI%20in%20Guwahati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaikia%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20said%20Rs%201.5%20lakh-crore%20investment%20will%20be%20made.%20This%20is%20a%20natural%20duty%20of%20a%20government.%20I%20hope%20that%20a%20new%20rich%20contractor%20class%20is%20not%20created%20out%20of%20this.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20underlined%20that%20the%20agreement%20has%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20Assam%20Accord%20of%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemanding%20that%20the%20government%20make%20the%20agreement%20public%2C%20CPI(M)%20Assam%20state%20secretary%20Suprakash%20Talukdar%20told%20PTI%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Assam%20CM%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20saying%20that%20without%20the%20participation%20of%20ULFA(I)%20chief%20Paresh%20Barua%20in%20this%20process%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20fructify.%20So%20what%20will%20be%20the%20outcome%20of%20this%20accord%3F%20Is%20the%20CM%20sticking%20to%20this%20position%20now%20also%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20pact%20%E2%80%9Cdisgusting%E2%80%9D%2C%20Raijor%20Dal%20President%20and%20MLA%20Akhil%20Gogoi%20wondered%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20peace%20agreement%20or%20an%20%E2%80%9Celection%20manifesto%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20not%20fulfilled%20any%20of%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Assamese%20people.%20Land%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20rights%2C%20culture%2C%20language%20and%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20of%20these%20have%20been%20protected%20through%20the%20pact%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20cadres%20have%20been%20in%20designated%20camps%20since%202008%2C%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20the%20ULFA%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20only%20in%202011%2C%20and%20has%20since%20been%20in%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Centre%20for%20a%20peace%20deal.%20Several%20times%2C%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20interlocutors%20have%20been%20changed%3B%20twice%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20break%20in%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UPA%20era%2C%20though%20the%20Rajkhowa%20group%20had%20shunned%20the%20demand%20to%20the%20Centre%20to%20discuss%20the%20sovereignty%E2%80%99%20issue%20of%20Assam%2C%20the%20Paresh%20Barua%20faction%20of%20the%20outfit%20%E2%80%93%20ULFA-Independent%20%E2%80%93%20has%20not.%20The%20Barua%20faction%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20smaller%20in%20size%20than%20the%20Rajkhowa%E2%80%99s%20overground%20faction%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20camping%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESigning%20the%20agreement%2C%20Rajkhowa%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20contribution%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20former%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Tarun%20Gogoi%20for%20having%20started%20the%20peace%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703919572000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fulfa-faction-signs-peace-accord-with-centre-political-gimmick-says-opposition-in-assam%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre%20in%20way%20back%20in%202011%2C%20several%20talks%20held%20since%20to%20work%20out%20a%20'peace%20deal'%20had%20failed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fulfa-faction-signs-peace-accord-with-centre-political-gimmick-says-opposition-in-assam%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Xi%20widens%20purge%2C%20abruptly%20ousts%209%20military%20lawmakers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703918402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106396950%2Cimgsize-25144.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fxi-jinping-continues-wi