%20density.%20The%20disappearance%20of%20agricultural%20lands%20has%20not%20only%20resulted%20in%20a%20scarcity%20of%20arable%20land%20but%20also%20displaced%20people%20from%20their%20primary%20economic%20activities.%20Census%20reports%20indicate%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20proportion%20of%20main%20workers%20within%20the%20rural%20workforce%2C%20coupled%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20proportion%20of%20marginal%20workers.%20Many%20families%20have%20migrated%20to%20cities%20like%20Gujarat%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Kerala%2C%20engaging%20in%20daily%20wage%20labour.%20Alarmingly%2C%20erosion%20has%20adversely%20affected%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20overall%20male%20literacy%20rate%20in%20these%20affected%20areas%20has%20decreased%20over%20the%20years%2C%20emphasising%20the%20extensive%20challenges%20faced%20by%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Farakka%20authority%20should%20distribute%20the%202%2C200%20bighas%20of%20land%20under%20their%20control%20among%20these%20landless%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20local%20labour%20activist%20Debajyoti%20Sinha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20see%20the%20light%20there%20%E2%80%93%20once%2C%20there%20was%20a%20school.%20I%20taught%20there%20for%2018%20years.%20There%20used%20to%20be%20three%20polling%20stations%2C%20everything%20was%20washed%20away.%20But%20when%20a%20new%20land%20rises%2C%20the%20government%20claims%20the%20right%20of%20that%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20local%20teacher%20Pranab%20Mondal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20programme%20Namami%20Gange%20has%20a%20budget%20outlay%20of%20Rs%2022%2C500%20crore%20from%202023%20to%202026%20to%20accomplish%20the%20twin%20objectives%20of%20effective%20abatement%20of%20pollution%2C%20conservation%20and%20rejuvenation%20of%20the%20Ganga.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20n