%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-2-1700658874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334675%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20pearls%20are%20cultivated%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20source%20good%20quality%20oysters.%20Then%2C%20we%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20The%20oyster%20is%20closed%20and%20is%20kept%20on%20antibiotics%20inside%20a%20smaller%20water%20tank%20for%20two%20to%20three%20days%20and%20then%20shifted%20to%20a%20bigger%20pond.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oyster%20then%20secretes%20nacre%20%5Ba%20form%20of%20calcium%20carbonate%5D%20around%20the%20nucleus.%20The%20pearls%20get%20readied%20to%20be%20harvested%20in%2012%20to%2014%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20shares%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20start%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20for%20beginners%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20identify%20good%20oysters%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20it%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20cultivate%20oysters%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20provided%20you%20cultivate%20good%20quality%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSource%20good%20quality%20oysters%20to%20get%20A-grade%20quality%20pearls.%20The%20si